e%20been%20killed%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20three-quarters%20of%20a%20million%20rendered%20homeless%2C%20fending%20for%20themselves%20under%20the%20open%20sky%2C%20with%20no%20food%2C%20water%2C%20electricity%2C%20medicines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fas-the-world-watches-gaza-has-become-a-graveyard-for-children%5C%22%3EAs%20the%20World%20Watches%2C%20Gaza%20Has%20Become%20a%20Graveyard%20for%20Children%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20may%20have%20feared%20being%20cornered%20by%20the%20bare-knuckled%20assault%2C%20but%20the%20politico-military%20group%20appears%20to%20be%20doing%20just%20fine%2C%20politically.%20The%20Netanyahu%20regime%20was%20left%20with%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20negotiate%20with%20it%20to%20secure%20the%20release%20of%20its%20kidnapped%20citizens%2C%20although%20the%20negotiation%20was%20conducted%20through%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fpolicy%2Finternational%2F4339181-netanyahu-pulls-negotiators-from-qatar%2F%5C%22%3EQatar%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20others%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F12%2F03%2Fworld%2Fmiddleeast%2Fisrael-hamas-hostages-gaza.html%5C%22%3Ethe%20US%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20civilian%20hostages%20abducted%20by%20Hamas%20fighters%20from%20Israel%20on%20October%207%20were%20to%20be%20released%20in%20batches%20in%20return%20for%20relief%20supplies%20and%20in%20exchange%20for%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20in%20Israeli%20prisons.%20On%20day%20two%20of%20the%20exchange%2C%20nervousness%20was%20caused%20when%20Hamas%2C%20for%20many%20hours%2C%20suspended%20the%20release%20of%20the%20Israeli%20detainees.%20The%20process%20resumed%20only%20after%20the%20agreed%20upon%20quantum%20of%20relief%20arrived%20in%20Gaza.%20This%20underlined%20the%20group%E2%80%99s%20salience%20and%20clout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2023%2F12%2F02%2F1216715999%2Fhow-israels-judicial-system-handles-the-estimated-7000-palestinians-in-its-priso%5C%22%3E7%2C000%20Palestinians%20in%20Israeli%20jails%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20are%20from%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20the%20only%20remaining%20Palestinian%20area%20other%20than%20Gaza.%20Disregarding%20numerous%20UN%20resolutions%20with%20America%E2%80%99s%20and%20Britain%E2%80%99s%20backing%2C%20Israel%20has%20been%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amnesty.org%2Fen%2Flatest%2Fcampaigns%2F2017%2F06%2Fisrael-occupation-50-years-of-dispossession%2F%5C%22%3Eillegal%20occupation%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%201967%20and%20runs%20it%20under%20police%20and%20military%20administration%20in%20the%20harshest%20manner%2C%20notwithstanding%20the%20notional%20control%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20over%20some%20of%20the%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20also%20settled%20some%20750%2C000%20Jewish%20settlers%20in%20this%20occupied%20region%2C%20forcibly%20chasing%20away%20the%20original%20Palestinian%20owners%20of%20the%20land%20over%20the%20decades.%20The%20Jerusalem%20area%2C%20deemed%20holy%20by%20three%20faiths%2C%20Judaism%2C%20Christianity%20and%20Islam%2C%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20administered%20internationally%20under%20the%20UN%20plan%20of%201947%20which%20partitioned%20the%20land%20of%20Palestine%20to%20permit%20the%20creation%20of%20Israel.%20Jerusalem%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpress.un.org%2Fen%2F2016%2Fsc12657.doc.htm%5C%22%3Ehas%20since%20been%20annexed%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0by%20Israel%20in%20violation%20of%20international%20agreements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaza%20was%20also%20under%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20illegal%20physical%20occupation%20from%201967%20to%202005%20when%20Israel%20pulled%20out%20of%20the%20territory.%20While%20doing%20so%2C%20it%20imposed%20a%20severe%20physical%20blockade%20from%20land%2C%20air%2C%20and%20sea%20on%20this%20coastal%20enclave%2C%20turning%20Gaza%20into%20what%E2%80%99s%20internationally%20regarded%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cworld%E2%80%99s%20largest%20open%20air%20prison%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20this%20background%2C%20West%20Bank%20residents%20in%20Israeli%20jails%20are%2C%20in%20reality%2C%20in%20the%20prisons%20of%20the%20occupiers%20of%20their%20lands.%20It%20is%20some%20of%20these%20prisoners%20who%20are%20now%20being%20set%20free%20by%20Israel%20in%20exchange%20for%20Israelis%20taken%20captive%20by%20Hamas%20during%20its%20October%207%20military%20raid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20on%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20including%20young%20girls%2C%20were%20jailed%20when%20they%20had%20not%20even%20reached%20their%20teens.%20Their%20%E2%80%9Ccrime%E2%80%9D%20was%20to%20throw%20stones%20at%20the%20occupation%20forces%20as%20a%20mark%20of%20resistance.%20What%E2%80%99s%20more%2C%20after%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20October%20strike%2C%20Israel%20imprisoned%20around%20200%20West%20Bank%20residents%2C%20apprehending%20them%20from%20the%20streets%2C%20and%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20even%20from%20their%20homes.%20News%20reports%20say%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F12%2F3%2Fhow-a-palestinian-teens-release-exposed-israeli-mistreatment-of-prisoners%5C%22%3Echarges%3C%2Fa%3E%20brought%20against%20them%20may%20be%20fabricated.%20This%20appears%20little%20different%20from%20the%20abduction%20of%20Israeli%20citizens%20by%20Hamas%20fighters%20on%20October%207%20which%20was%20widely%20seen%20as%20an%20act%20of%20%E2%80%9Cterrorism%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22162028%2Fgaza-israel-barrier.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22162028%2Fgaza-israel-barrier.jpg%201000w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22162028%2Fgaza-israel-barrier-300x184.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685931%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22614%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20barrier%20between%20Israel%20and%20Gaza.%20Photo%3A%20%C2%A0IDF%20Spokesperson%E2%80%99s%20Unit%2C%20Wikimedia%20Commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20is%20a%20Palestinian%20entity%20from%20Gaza%2C%20but%20its%20stock%20appears%20to%20have%20soared%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20following%20the%20release%20of%20West%20Bank%20prisoners.%20On%20the%20first%20day%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fgallery%2F2023%2F12%2F1%2Fphotos-palestinians-celebrate-release-of-another-batch-of-prisoners%5C%22%3Eprisoner%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20ordinary%20people%20on%20West%20Bank%20streets%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fpalestinians-israel-prisoner-exchange-hostage-92545883b1fef86fb9b34549b7deca58%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edraped%20themselves%20in%20Hamas%20flags%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20Fatah%20faction%20of%20what%E2%80%99s%20now%20the%20disintegrated%20Palestinian%20Liberation%20Organisation%20(PLO)%2C%20led%20by%20the%20once%20redoubtable%20Yasser%20Arafat%2C%20enjoys%20only%20nominal%20authority%20now%2C%20and%20evidently%20little%20public%20esteem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETechnically%2C%20it%20still%20runs%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20(PA).%20But%20the%20question%20is%3A%20Where%20is%20the%20PA%20when%20the%20West%20Bank%20and%20Jerusalem%20are%20under%20Israeli%20jackboots%3F%20The%20PA%20appeared%20to%20be%20pretty%20much%20somnolent%20after%20the%20watershed%20incident%20of%20October%207%2C%20although%20to%20their%20credit%2C%20the%20PA%20ambassadors%20in%20London%20and%20New%20Delhi%20forcefully%20conveyed%20the%20anguish%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20and%20the%20colonial%20brutality%20of%20Israel%20even%20when%20the%20media%20set%20out%20to%20seek%20from%20them%20a%20condemnation%20of%20Hamas%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cterrorist%E2%80%9D%20outfit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-hamas-karan-thapar-paola-caridi-interview%5C%22%3EWatch%20%7C%20Everything%20You%20Need%20to%20Know%20About%20Hamas%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Celimination%E2%80%9D%20of%20Hamas%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20brief%20pause%20and%20the%20resulting%20hostages%20and%20prisoners%20exchange%2C%20was%20not%20going%20to%20lead%20to%20a%20comprehensive%20ceasefire%20and%20the%20cessation%20of%20hostilities%20by%20the%20Netanhayu%20government%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20peace%20formulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20the%20Israeli%20government%E2%80%99s%20goal%20is%20clearly%20ill-conceived%20as%20it%20is%20impossible%20to%20accomplish.%20Powerful%20ideas%2C%20such%20as%20the%20fight%20against%20colonial%20oppression%20and%20foreign%20occupation%2C%20live%20through%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20relentless%20bombardment%20of%20Gaza%2C%20including%20its%20most%20important%20hospitals%2C%20the%20Israeli%20state%20is%20now%20being%20questioned%20on%20moral%20grounds.%20People%20around%20the%20world%20have%20refused%20to%20accept%20false%20Israeli%20propaganda%20%E2%80%93%20that%20Hamas%20was%20using%20the%20famous%20al-Shifa%20hospital%20as%20a%20military%20command%20and%20control%20centre%20%E2%80%93%20as%20a%20justification%20for%20its%20targeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20has%20to%20be%20a%20%3Cem%3Eschmuck%3C%2Fem%3E%20not%20to%20see%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeading%20governments%20of%20the%20South%2C%20such%20as%20Brazil%20and%20South%20Africa%2C%20and%20several%20others%2C%20have%20downgraded%20or%20even%20cut%20off%20diplomatic%20ties%20with%20Israel.%20However%2C%20India%2C%20under%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20is%20an%20exception%20among%20non-Western%20powers.%20It%20has%20demonstrated%20unquestioning%20support%20for%20the%20Netanyahu%20regime%20and%20its%20relentless%20military%20assault%20on%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20influential%20Western%20circles%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20US%2C%20it%20is%20being%20posited%20that%20Israel%20has%20placed%20itself%20on%20the%20same%20plane%20as%20Hamas%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20decried%20as%20%E2%80%9Cterrorist%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20by%20bombarding%20the%20unarmed%20civilian%20population%20of%20Gaza.%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20standing%20four-square%20behind%20the%20Israeli%20action%2C%20has%20not%20only%20discredited%20himself%20but%2C%20quite%20possibly%2C%20ensured%20the%20loss%20of%20support%20in%20the%20large%20constituency%20of%20the%20young%20in%20the%202024%20presidential%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArab%20governments%20that%20were%20until%20recently%20moving%20toward%20an%20economic%20and%20political%20rapprochement%20with%20Israel%20under%20US%20inducement%20and%20facilitation%2C%20leaving%20the%20Palestine%20question%20hanging%20fire%2C%20are%20showing%20signs%20of%20holding%20back.%20They%20are%20only%20too%20keenly%20aware%20of%20the%20strong%20anti-Israel%20and%20anti-US%20sentiment%20sweeping%20through%20public%20opinion%20in%20their%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Palestinian%20side%2C%20it%20is%20Hamas%20which%20is%20now%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20things%2C%20not%20Fatah%20or%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20of%20President%20Abbas%2C%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20recent%20best%20efforts%20of%20Israel%20and%20the%20US%20to%20bring%20the%20PA%20into%20play.%20While%20Hamas%20appears%20to%20have%20emerged%20as%20the%20new%20hope%20of%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20the%20political%20star%20of%20Netanyahu%20can%20fairly%20be%20said%20to%20be%20in%20decline.%20There%20is%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20weighty%20speculation%20in%20Israel%20that%20the%20prime%20m