0of%20an%20idea%20can%20only%20be%20called%20a%20fool%E2%80%99s%20errand.%20In%20reality%2C%20if%20not%20today%2C%20then%20some%20other%20day%2C%20it%20is%20Hamas%20with%20which%20those%20interested%20in%20eventually%20negotiating%20the%20complex%20Palestinian%20question%20will%20have%20to%20deal.%20This%20includes%20Israel%2C%20the%20US%2C%20and%20the%20prominent%20Arab%20countries%20%E2%80%93%20Netanyahu%20or%20no%20Netanyahu%2C%20Biden%20or%20no%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20so-called%20objective%20of%20eliminating%20Hamas%20is%20a%20red%20herring.%20The%20real%2C%20hidden%20aim%20behind%20keeping%20up%20the%20military%20attack%20appears%20to%20be%20to%20drive%20out%20the%20Palestinians%20from%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20%E2%80%93%20giving%20effect%20to%20a%20second%20%3Cem%3Enaqba%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20first%20%3Cem%3Enaqba%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20in%201948%20when%20Palestinians%20were%20driven%20out%20of%20their%20land%20upon%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20state%20of%20Israel.%20And%20now%20they%20are%20to%20be%20driven%20out%20of%20the%20lands%20to%20which%20they%20were%20forced%20to%20flee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20mocks%20history%20when%20the%20Israel%20leadership%2C%20and%20echoing%20with%20them%20the%20North%20Americans%20and%20the%20West%20Europeans%20and%20their%20current%20allies%2C%20the%20Indians%2C%20says%20it%20has%20the%20%E2%80%9Cright%20to%20defend%20itself%E2%80%9D.%20The%20question%20is%20from%20whom%3F%20From%20the%20people%20whose%20land%20it%20has%20occupied%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fanand-k-sahay%5C%22%3EAnand%20K.%20Sahay%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20political%20commentator%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701783918000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01111519%2Fimage1170x530cropped.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisraels-hamas-red-herring-evicting-pale