t%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6565d514c58b6f84123ad79a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222592%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERiley%20Reid%20is%20an%20adult-content%20star%20and%20OnlyFans%20creator.%3Cp%3EGabe%20Ginsberg%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAdult-content%20and%20OnlyFans%20star%20Riley%20Reid%20has%20created%20an%20AI%20chatbot%20based%20on%20herself.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20tech%2C%20now%20in%20beta%2C%20will%20soon%20allow%20other%20creators%20to%20build%20%26quot%3Bdigital%20copies%26quot%3B%20of%20themselves.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EReid%20said%20she%20sees%20AI%20as%20a%20way%20to%20%26quot%3Bimmortalize%26quot%3B%20herself%20and%20interact%20with%20fans%20for%20years%20to%20come.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20adult-content%20and%20OnlyFans%20star%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonlyfans-creators-pay-each-other-millions-of-dollars-gain-followers-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERiley%20Reid%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently%20launched%20an%20AI%20platform%2C%20Clona%2C%20with%20a%20chatbot%20based%20on%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReid%20said%20the%20rise%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-ai-100-2023-the-people-who-make-ai-intelligent-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20give%20her%20the%20chance%20to%20build%20relationships%20with%20her%20fans%20without%20sacrificing%20her%20personal%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20married.%20I'm%20a%20mother.%20I'm%20trying%20to%20do%20multiple%20businesses%2C%26quot%3B%20Reid%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThis%20gives%20me%20an%20opportunity%20to%20immortalize%20myself%20and%20still%20be%20in%20that%20field%20without%20investing%20my%20full%20self.%20I%20feel%20so%20lucky%20I've%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20create%20Riley%20Reid%20as%20a%20mainstream%20name.%20I%20really%20want%20to%20utilize%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReid%20has%20been%20in%20the%20industry%20for%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20primarily%20shooting%20mainstream%20adult%20content%2C%20and%20said%20she'd%20never%20had%20much%20interaction%20with%20her%20fans.%20Even%20when%20she%20got%20onto%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-money-onlyfans-creators-make-real-examples-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOnlyFans%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20chatting%20with%20creators%20is%20a%20key%20feature%2C%20she%20mostly%20kept%20her%20privacy%2C%20and%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20make%20time%20to%20respond%20and%20communicate%20with%20all%20her%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReid%20said%20she%20envisioned%20AI%20as%20a%20way%20to%20make%20this%20easier%2C%20and%20allow%20her%20fans%20to%20interact%20with%20her%20on%20a%20personal%20level%20for%20decades%20to%20come%2C%20even%20when%20she%20decides%20to%20stop%20shooting%20videos%2C%20or%20gets%20too%20busy%20with%20other%20projects%20%E2%80%94%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eighteenplusclothing.com%2Fpages%2Fcontact%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclothing%20brand%3C%2Fa%3E%20she%20founded%20with%20her%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Adult%20content%20creator%20Riley%20Reid%20wearing%20a%20white%20blazer%2C%20standing%20on%20a%20balcony.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6569b82058e7c0c29a289bf9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERiley%20Reid%20has%20been%20in%20the%20adult-content%20industry%20for%20over%20a%20decade.%3Cp%3EClona%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20Clona%20was%20built%2C%20and%20how%20it%20works%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EClona%20is%20currently%20in%20beta%2C%20and%20offers%20chatbots%20for%20Reid%20and%20Lena%20The%20Plug%2C%20another%20adult-content%20creator.%20Reid%20cofounded%20Clona%20based%20on%20an%20idea%20her%20team%20had%20when%20they%20began%20noticing%20the%20success%20of%20AI%20chatbots%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-creators-think-about-ai-impact-on-influencer-work-survey-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20partnered%20with%20a%20team%20engineers%20and%20programmers%20to%20build%20a%20product%20that%20would%20reflect%20Reid's%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsers%20can%20exchange%20five%20messages%20with%20the%20chatbots%20for%20free%3B%20for%20unlimited%20chatting%20and%20voice%20notes%2C%20the%20service%20costs%20%2430%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20platform%20was%20created%20using%20a%20proprietary%20large-language%20model%20based%20on%20Meta's%20Llama%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bheavily%20modified%20and%20fine-tuned%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20company%20spokesperson%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-paying-celebrity-faces-of-ai-chatbots-as-much-as-5-million-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently%20launched%20its%20own%20AI%20chatbots%20that%20are%20loosely%20based%20on%20celebrities%20like%20Paris%20Hilton%20and%20Tom%20Brady.%20For%20example%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2FAmberTheDetective%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHilton's%20AI%20%3C%2Fa%3Eversion%20is%20a%20true-crime%20lover%20and%20detective%20called%20Amber%2C%20while%20Brady's%20is%20Bru%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bwisecracking%20sports%20debater%20who%20pulls%20no%20punches%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20Meta%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabout.fb.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F09%2Fintroducing-ai-powered-assistants-characters-and-creative-tools%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblog%20post%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClona%20is%20different%2C%20and%20made%20to%20replicate%20the%20experience%20of%20chatting%20to%20real-life%20creators%2C%20rather%20than%20offering%20a%20new%20fictional%20character%20based%20on%20an%20existing%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20create%20a%20chatbot%20that%20would%20resemble%20Reid%20as%20closely%20as%20possible%2C%20the%20AI%20was%20fed%20hundreds%20of%20hours%20of%20her%20audio%20and%20video%20content%2C%20from%20podcast%20interviews%20to%20adult%20scenes%2C%20along%20with%20the%20entirety%20of%20her%20social-media%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReid%20also%20fact-checked%20its%20output%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20it%20would%20represent%20her%20accurately%2C%20and%20that%20it%20would%20approach%20certain%20topics%2C%20like%20thorny%20political%20or%20social%20issues%2C%20in%20a%20firm%20but%20polite%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20my%20biggest%20things%20is%2C%20I%20believe%20that%20trans%20people%20should%20have%20rights%2C%26quot%3B%20Reid%20said.%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20is%20entitled%20to%20their%20own%20opinion%2C%20but%20I%20have%20my%20own%20political%20beliefs.%20If%20someone%20says%20something%20that%20is%20anti%20trans%2C%20or%20transphobic%2C%20how%20does%20my%20AI%20respond%20in%20a%20politically%20correct%20way%20that%20says%20like%2C%20'Hey%2C%20I%20don't%20agree%2C%20I%20love%20the%20trans%20community'%3F%20I%20don't%20want%20my%20AI%20to%20just%20skip%20over%20trans%20rights%2C%20I%20want%20her%20to%20have%20my%20actual%20opinion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20chatbot%20is%20meant%20to%20replicate%20Reid's%20personality%2C%20the%20creator%20also%20wanted%20users%20to%20be%20able%20to%20cater%20to%20their%20own%20desires.%20Unlike%20the%20%26quot%3BRiley%20Reid%26quot%3B%20character%20that%20she%20embodies%20in%20adult%20movies%2C%20which%20has%20always%20stayed%20pretty%20much%20the%20same%2C%20with%20the%20similar%20appearance%20and%20%26quot%3Bgirl-next-door%26quot%3B%20roles%2C%20the%20AI%20will%20be%20more%20customizable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRiley%20is%20a%20persona%2C%20and%20from%20this%20persona%20that%20you%20fantasize%20about%20you're%20able%20to%20create%20a%20version%20that%20is%20more%20suitable%20to%20your%20specific%20needs%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20request%20your%20AI%20Riley%20to%20give%20herself%20a%20purple%20mohawk%20if%20that's%20what%20you're%20into%2C%20because%20real-life%20Riley%20would%20never%20do%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EReid%20says%20fans%20will%20be%20able%20to%20build%20a%20'form%20of%20human%20connection'%20with%20the%20AI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20open%20up%20the%20platform%20to%20any%20creator%20or%20celebrity%20who%20wishes%20to%20create%20a%20%26quot%3Bdigital%20copy%26quot%3B%20of%20themselves%20in%20the%20future%2C%20but%20that%20the%20team%20is%20still%20working%20on%20refining%20the%20AI%20model%20and%20understanding%20the%20reaction%20from%20the%20public.%20Reid%20added%20that%20because%20the%20AI%20needs%20to%20be%20trained%20to%20resemble%20the%20real%20person%20closely%2C%20the%20process%20of%20refining%20it%20can%20be%20time%20consuming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERunning%20a%20proprietary%20large-language%20model%20is%20also%20expensive%2C%20and%20the%20company%20is%20looking%20to%20cut%20costs%2C%20which%20currently%20sit%20at%20about%20%2430%2C000%20a%20month%20just%20for%20cloud%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20thousands%20of%20users%20have%20been%20testing%20the%20platform.%20The%20Clona%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20company%20had%20been%20surprised%20at%20the%20type%20of%20intimate%20relationships%20that%20users%20had%20already%20built%20with%20the%20AI%2C%20and%20the%20companionship%20that%20had%20resulted%20from%20it%20%E2%80%94%20beyond%20the%20interactions%20based%20on%20sexual%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20like%20that%20my%20AI%20has%20a%20form%20of%20human%20connection%20because%20she's%20based%20off%20of%20a%20real%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20Reid%20said.%20%26quot%3BShe%20has%20my%20life%20and%20everything.%20People%20always%20care%20for%20human%20connection%2C%20and%20that's%20always%20going%20to%20exist.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadult-content-onlyfans-star-riley-reid-ai-chatbot-fans-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701782425000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6565d52ffe5bc6545ebcd558%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadult-content-onlyfans-star-riley-reid-ai-chatbot-fans-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20technology%20interacts%20with%20users%20the%20same%20way%20the%20creator%20would.%20It's%20based%20on%20hundreds%20of%20hours%20of%20Reid's%20content%2C%20and%20fact-checked%20by%20her.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mbiino%40insider.com%20(Marta%20Biino)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A180%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadult-content-onlyfans-star-riley-reid-ai-chatbot-fans-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Revanth%20Reddy%20to%20be%20next%20Telangana%20CM%3B%20oath-taking%20ceremony%20on%20Dec%207%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701782382000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-08%2F28%2Ffull%2F1693246245-4311.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Felections%2Ftelangana-elections%2Ftelangana-assembly-election-tpcc-chief-revanth-reddy-likely-to-be-next-cm-123120500383_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Revanth%20Reddy%20contested%20from%20both%20Kodangal%20and%20Kamareddy.%20He%20won%20the%20the%20Kodangal%20seat%20with%20a%2032%2C532%20vote%20margin.%20The%20oath%20taking%20ceremony%20will%20take%20place%20on%20December%207%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Felections%2Ftelangana-elections%2Ftelangana-assembly-election-tpcc-chief-revanth-reddy-likely-to-be-next-cm-123120500383_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bu