023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eluxury%20travel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20this%20sweet%20deal%20was%20completely%20worth%20the%20extra%20money%20spent.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20believe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fvirgin-atlantic-business-class-flight-experience-photos-worth-it-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflying%20business%20class%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20epitome%20of%20luxury.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20avid%20travelers%2C%20we%20take%20at%20least%20one%20international%20trip%20every%20year%20and%20often%20look%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fqatar-airways-business-class-flight-experience-photos-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeals%20on%20business-class%20tickets%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20my%20husband%2C%20son%2C%20and%20I%20flew%20round%20trip%20from%20New%20Delhi%20to%20London%20on%20Virgin%20Atlantic's%20business%20class%2C%20which%20the%20company%20refers%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Bupper%20class.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20having%20a%20great%20experience%2C%20we%20hoped%20to%20once%20again%20score%20upper-class%20tickets%20on%20the%20same%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20because%20this%20year's%20prices%20were%20too%20high%20at%20824%2C700%20rupees%20(about%20%249%2C900)%2C%20we%20made%20peace%20with%20booking%20premium%20economy%20round-trip%20tickets%20for%20389%2C150%20rupees%20(%244%2C600).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20weeks%20later%2C%20while%20on%20Virgin%20Atlantic's%20website%2C%20my%20husband%20came%20across%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.virginatlantic.com%2Fcn%2Fen%2Ftravel-information%2Fextras-and-upgrades%2Fyour-bid.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYour%20Bid%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20program%2C%20which%20allows%20passengers%20to%20bid%20for%20an%20upgrade%20to%20premium-%20or%20upper-class%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20minimum%20bidding%20amount%20kept%20changing%2C%20but%20when%20my%20husband%20placed%20his%20bid%2C%20the%20minimum%20amount%20per%20upper-class%20ticket%20was%2050%2C000%20rupees%20(%24600)%20for%20our%20flight%20from%20New%20Delhi%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Flondon-best-places-instagram-photos-2020-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELondon%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20our%20return%20flight%2C%20the%20minimum%20bid%20was%2047%2C000%20rupees%20(%24560)%20per%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdding%201%2C000%20rupees%20(%2412)%20to%20the%20minimum%20bid%20each%20way%2C%20my%20husband%20decided%20to%20give%20it%20a%20shot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EForty-eight%20hours%20before%20our%20scheduled%20departure%2C%20Virgin%20Atlantic%20emailed%20us%20that%20our%20bid%20for%20upper-class%20tickets%20had%20been%20accepted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20total%2C%20we%20paid%20684%2C350%20rupees%20(roughly%20%248%2C200)%20round%20trip%20for%20two%20adults%20and%20a%20child%2C%20including%20the%20price%20of%20original%20premium-economy%20tickets%20and%20two%20bid%20upgrades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20saved%20roughly%20%241%2C700%20through%20the%20bidding%20process%20and%20were%20excited%20to%20begin%20our%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20plane's%20interiors%20were%20spacious%20and%20luxurious%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Noor%20Anand%20Chawla%20and%20her%20husband%20holding%20drinks%20and%20smiling%20in%20business-class.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6557a1cd36d588dc55d271a7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20cabin%20was%20comfortable%20and%20spacious.%20%3Cp%3ENoor%20Anand%20Chawla%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20flights%20had%20a%20herringbone%20design%20in%20the%20upper-class%20cabin%2C%20with%20three%20rows%20of%20about%2010%20seats%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20son%20were%20assigned%20window%20seats%2C%20and%20I%20had%20a%20middle%20seat%20close%20to%20my%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20settling%20into%20our%20seats%2C%20the%20flight%20attendants%20brought%20us%20welcome%20drinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOur%20meals%20were%20tasty%20and%20customizable%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20plate%20of%20Indian%20food%20and%20two%20gold%20salt%20and%20pepper%20shakers%20that%20look%20like%20airplanes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6557a89236d588dc55d27b4b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20really%20enjoyed%20all%20of%20the%20in-flight%20meals%20%3Cp%3ENoor%20Anand%20Chawla%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20flight%20attendants%20asked%20for%20our%20meal%20preferences%20while%20we%20waited%20for%20take-off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20chose%20to%20skip%20the%20starter%20and%20dessert%20but%20asked%20for%20sourdough%20bread%2C%20which%20they%20fortunately%20had%20on%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20one%20course%2C%20I%20had%20chicken%20achari%20curry%2C%20served%20with%20cabbage%20and%20carrot%20thoran%2C%20basmati%20rice%2C%20and%20paratha.%20It%20was%20filling%20and%20not%20spicy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20enjoyed%20the%20cheese%20plate%20with%20Snowdonia%20Rock%20Star%20cave-aged%20cheddar%2C%20Blacksticks%20blue%2C%20Somerset%20camembert%20with%20grapes%2C%20sundried%20tomato%20and%20red-pepper%20chutney%2C%20and%20crackers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20request%2C%20they%20provided%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fbest-and-worst-pasta-dishes-to-order-at-restaurant%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplate%20of%20pasta%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20bread%20and%20fruit%20for%20my%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20my%20final%20meal%2C%20I%20chose%20the%20vegetable%20Indian%20platter%20consisting%20of%20aloo%20tikki%2C%20vegetable%20samosa%2C%20pepper%20pakora%2C%20and%20a%20tomato%20and%20onion%20salad%20with%20sweet-chili-and-tomato%20chutney.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20spacious%20seating%20was%20great%20for%20work%