D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Revanth%20Reddy%20Will%20Be%20Telangana%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20Confirms%20Rahul%20Gandhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F05182152%2Frahul-revanth.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20face%20of%20the%20Congress%20campaign%20in%20Telangana%2C%20Anumula%20Revanth%20Reddy%2C%20has%20been%20chosen%20as%20the%20new%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20southern%20state%2C%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20December%205.%20He%20will%20be%20sworn%20in%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20decision%20was%20taken%20at%20a%20meeting%20attended%20by%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20party%E2%80%99s%20general%20secretary%20(organisation)%20K.C.%20Venugopal%2C%20apart%20from%20leaders%20like%20D.K.%20Shivakumar%20who%20apparently%20conveyed%20to%20the%20central%20leadership%20that%20a%20majority%20of%20newly-elected%20legislators%20in%20the%20state%20preferred%20Revath%20Reddy%20over%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftelangana-news%2Fcongress-revanth-reddy-to-be-telangana-chief-minister-sources-4635221%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_bigstory%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENDTV%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reported%20that%2042%20of%20the%2064%20Congress%20MLAs%20supported%20Revanth%20Reddy.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20decided%20to%20conduct%20the%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20on%20December%206%2C%20which%20was%20postponed%20following%20%E2%80%9Cobjections%E2%80%9D%20to%20Revanth%E2%80%99s%20candidature.%20Reports%20said%20that%20leaders%20like%20former%20Congress%20legislature%20party%20(CLP)%20leader%20Bhatti%20Vikramarka%2C%20former%20Congress%20state%20chief%20N.%20Uttam%20Kumar%20Reddy%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eformer%20minister%20Komatireddy%20Venkat%20Reddy%2C%20former%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Damodar%20Raja%20Narasimha%20were%20among%20those%20who%20opposed%20Revanth%20Reddy%20on%20grounds%20that%20he%20had%20corruption%20cases%20against%20him%20and%20could%20not%20deliver%20a%20majority%20of%20assembly%20seats%20in%20his%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20Malkajgiri.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20of%20these%20leaders%20had%20also%20opposed%20Revanth%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20and%20called%20him%20a%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%20implant%20in%20the%20Congress.%20Revanth%20Reddy%20had%20joined%20the%20Congress%20from%20the%20TDP%20and%20was%20considered%20close%20to%20N.%20Chandrababu%20Naidu.%20He%20had%20begun%20his%20political%20career%20as%20an%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Vidyarthi%20Parishad%20leader%2C%20traversing%20through%20many%20parties%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Ftelangana%2Fwho-is-revanth-reddy-the-man-who-has-dethroned-kcr-in-telangana%5C%22%3Eincluding%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Telangana%20(now%20Bharat)%20Rashtra%20Samithi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20was%20made%20the%20Congress%20party%E2%80%99s%20state%20unit%20chief%20in%202021%2C%20soon%20after%20joining.%20In%20his%20role%20as%20the%20PCC%20president%2C%20he%20organised%20multiple%20rallies%20in%20which%20he%20aggressively%20attacked%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrashekhar%20Rao%20(KCR)%20and%20his%20government%20for%20failing%20to%20meet%20people%E2%80%99s%20expectations.%20The%20strategy%20worked%20in%20reviving%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20dislodged%20the%20BJP%20which%20was%20fast%20emerging%20as%20the%20primary%20opposition%20party%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20central%20leadership%E2%80%99s%20decision%20swayed%20towards%20Revanth%20Reddy%20as%20his%20energetic%20leadership%20is%20credited%20with%20reviving%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20fortunes%20in%20Telangana%2C%20where%20it%20was%20down%20and%20out%20after%20a%20majority%20of%20MLAs%20in%20the%20last%20assembly%20merged%20with%20the%20BRS.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReddy%20does%20not%20come%20from%20a%20political%20family%2C%20as%20is%20usually%20the%20norm%20among%20top-rung%20leaders%20in%20the%20Telugu%20states.%20He%20is%2C%20however%2C%20married%20to%20Geetha%2C%20the%20niece%20of%20late%20Congress%20leader%20and%20former%20Union%20minister%20S.%20Jaipal%20Reddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20he%20was%20caught%20in%20a%20%E2%80%98sting%20operation%E2%80%99%20while%20offering%20to%20bribe%20a%20nominated%20legislator%20to%20cast%20his%20vote%20for%20a%20TDP%20MLC.%20The%20case%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20Damocles%20sword%20hung%20above%20his%20head%20by%20KCR%2C%20but%20Reddy%20has%20nevertheless%20managed%20to%20climb%20to%20the%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBhatti%20Vikramarka%20and%20N.%20Uttam%20Kumar%20Reddy%2C%20both%20of%20whom%20also%20played%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20victory%2C%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20made%20deputy%20chief%20ministers.%20Vikramarka%20led%20a%201500-km-long%20foot%20rally%20in%20the%20state%2C%20while%20Uttam%20Reddy%20consolidated%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20ranks%20and%20helped%20the%20party%20mount%20an%20effective%20campaign%20against%20the%20popular%20KCR.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701781185000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F05182152%2Frahul-revanth.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frevanth-reddy-telangana-chief-minister-rahul-gandhi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20reports%2C%2042%20of%20the%2064%20Congress%20MLAs%20supported%20Revanth%20Reddy%20despite%20some%20influential%20leaders%20opposing%20his%20candidature.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frevanth-reddy-telangana-chief-minister-rahul-gandhi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22tit