A712B4.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20Jewish%20girl%20growing%20up%20in%20provincial%20England%20then%20Italy%2C%20%C2%A0I%20grew%20accustomed%20to%20anti-Semitism.%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20be%20Jewey!%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20playground%20when%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20share%20sweets.%20%E2%80%9CSteen%3F%20Don%E2%80%99t%20you%20mean%20Stein%3F%E2%80%9D%20when%20I%20told%20teachers%20my%20mother%E2%80%99s%20maiden%20name.%20And%20over%20and%20over%3A%20%E2%80%9CYou%20don%E2%80%99t%20look%20Jewish%E2%80%9D%20though%20my%20blonde%2C%20snub-nosed%20looks%20make%20me%20a%20ringer%20for%20my%20Polish%20grandmother.%20One%20elderly%20Italian%20lady%20told%20me%20that%20she%20thought%20Jews%20struggled%20with%20Nazis%20because%20they%20were%20similar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20occasions%20are%20upsetting%20but%20I%20have%20never%20felt%20unsafe.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20experience%20of%20many%20Jews.%20If%20you%20attend%20synagogue%20and%20if%20your%20appearance%20marks%20you%20as%20Jewish%2C%20such%20badges%20of%20belonging%20make%20you%20a%20target.%20Since%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20attack%20of%20October%207%2C%20and%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20retaliation%2C%20reports%20of%20anti-Semitic%20attacks%20have%20soared%20in%20Europe%20and%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Islamophobia%20is%20also%20ever-present.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2021%2F03%2F1086452%5C%22%3E2021%20report%20by%20the%20UN%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20it%20is%20rising%20worldwide.%20The%20victory%20of%20anti-Islamic%20politician%20Geert%20Wilders%20in%20the%20Dutch%20elections%20mirrors%20the%20success%20of%20populist%20leaders%20such%20as%20Trump%20and%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Since%20October%207%2C%20that%20hatred%20has%20intensified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fthe-right-wing-is-on-the-rise-globally%5C%22%3EThe%20Right%20Wing%20Is%20on%20the%20Rise%20Globally%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEquality%20and%20justice%20are%20collective%20operations.%20It%20is%20unjust%20to%20Muslims%20when%20governments%20and%20institutions%20fail%20to%20tackle%20Islamophobia%20with%20the%20same%20ferocity%20with%20which%20they%20tackle%20anti-Semitism.%20But%20it%20also%20endangers%20Jews%20because%20it%20suggests%20they%20deserve%20special%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conflation%20of%20anti-Zionism%20with%20anti-Semitism%20is%20also%20dangerous.%20There%20is%20an%20irrationality%20coiled%20within%20a%20concept%20that%20states%20Israel%20and%20Jewishness%20are%20the%20same%20thing.%20There%20is%20an%20old%20Jewish%20joke%20about%20one%20Jew%20needing%20two%20synagogues%3A%20the%20one%20he%20goes%20to%20and%20the%20one%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t.%20There%20are%20a%20myriad%20ways%20of%20being%20Jewish.%20Many%20of%20us%20identify%20as%20Jewish%20but%20also%20as%20a%20cornucopia%20of%20other%20things.%20To%20riff%20on%20the%20US%20poet%20Walt%20Whitman%2C%20Jews%20%E2%80%93%20like%20everyone%20else%20%E2%80%93%20contain%20multitudes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20culture%20sector%20is%20cracking%20under%20the%20weight%20of%20this%20unreason.%20Recently%20international%20dealer%20Lisson%20Gallery%20cancelled%20a%20show%20by%20Ai%20Weiwei%20after%20a%20tweet%20which%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theartnewspaper.com%2F2023%2F11%2F14%2Flisson-gallery-pulls-ai-weiwei-london-show-over-israel-hamas-war-tweet%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.theartnewspaper.com%2F2023%2F11%2F14%2Flisson-gallery-pulls-ai-weiwei-london-show-over-israel-hamas-war-tweet%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1701767731362000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2G3OuOrLPwOokhcBsemPF4%5C%22%3Ereportedly%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0stated%3A%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9CFinancially%2C%20culturally%2C%20and%20in%20terms%20of%20media%20influence%2C%20the%20Jewish%20community%20has%20had%20a%20significant%20presence%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20The%20annual%20%243%20billion%20aid%20package%20to%20Israel%20has%2C%20for%20decades%2C%20been%20touted%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20valuable%20investments%20the%20United%20States%20has%20ever%20made.%20This%20partnership%20is%20often%20described%20as%20one%20of%20shared%20destiny%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWeiwei%20seemed%20to%20conflate%20Jewishness%20with%20Zionism.%20Furthermore%2C%20by%20implying%20that%20the%20Jewish%20community%20is%20a%20powerful%2C%20homogenous%20entity%2C%20he%20risked%20falling%20into%20anti-Semitic%20tropes%20that%20the%20Jews%20run%20Hollywood%20and%20Congress%20and%20are%20plotting%20world%20domination.%20Certainly%2C%20there%20are%20powerful%20Jews%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20There%20are%20many%20powerless%20ones%20too.%20Some%20support%20Israel.%20Many%20don%E2%80%99t.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Weiwei%20deleted%20his%20tweet.%20Given%20that%2C%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20Lisson%20have%20gone%20ahead%3F%20One%20erased%20tweet%2C%20from%20an%20artist%20indubitably%20committed%20to%20justice%2C%20does%20not%20make%20a%20pogrom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20parallels%20to%20be%20drawn%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2022%2F07%2F16%2Farts%2Fdesign%2Fdocumenta-resignation.html%5C%22%3Elast%20year%E2%80%99s%20debacle%20at%20the%20German%20contemporary%20arts%20festival%20Documenta%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20it%20became%20embroiled%20in%20accusations%20of%20anti-Semitism%20stoked%20by%20a%20government%20which%20fails%20to%20distinguish%20between%20Zionism%20and%20Judaism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20baffling%20decisions%20have%20followed.%20For%20Documenta%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.artnews.com%2Fart-news%2Fnews%2Fdocumenta-denounces-selection-committee-member-bds-letter-israel-palestine-1234686372%2F%5C%22%3Eaccuse%20committee%20member%20Ranjit%20Hoskot%C3%A9%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20most%20sensitive%20of%20thinkers%2C%20of%20anti-Semitism%20is%20to%20drive%20out%20exactly%20the%20kind%20of%20reflective%2C%20nuanced%20voice%20that%20culture%20needs.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theartnewspaper.com%2F2023%2F11%2F22%2Fgerman-photo-biennial-cancelled-after-curators-posts-are-deemed-antisemitic%23%5C%22%3EA%20photography%20biennale%20actually%20cancelled%20itself%3C%2Fa%3E%20rather%20than%20permit%20curation%20by%20photojournalist%2C%20teacher%20and%20activist%20Shahidul%20Alam%20whom%20they%20dubbed%20anti-Semitic%20for%20describing%20the%20situation%20in%20Gaza%20as%20a%20genocide%20and%20comparing%20it%20to%20the%20Holocaust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Fwhat-explains-the-political-rights-ascendancy-to-global-power%5C%22%3EWhat%20Explains%20the%20Political%20Right%E2%80%99s%20Ascendancy%20to%20Global%20Power%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who%20knows%20Alam%20well%2C%20I%20can%20verify%20that%20he%20is%20not%20anti-Semitic.%20His%20courage%2C%20wisdom%20and%20humanity%20have%20been%20proven%20time%20and%20again%20not%20least%20when%20he%20went%20to%20prison%20for%20criticising%20his%20own%20government%20in%20Bangladesh.%20If%20I%20were%20in%20danger%20from%20anti-Semitism%20%E2%80%93%20or%20anything%20else%20%E2%80%93%20it%E2%80%99s%20Alam%20I%20would%20want%20at%20my%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlam%20and%20I%20may%20debate%20his%20posts.%20I%20try%20to%20avoid%20comparisons%20between%20different%20atrocities%20because%20I%20believe%20that%20specificity%20is%20intrinsic%20to%20solutions.%20He%20and%20I%20will%20probably%2C%20as%20we%20have%20before%2C%20agree%20to%20differ.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArt%20should%20be%20a%20space%20where%20differences%20are%20permitted%20freedom.%20Art%20springs%20from%20friction.%20From%20contradiction%2C%20paradox%2C%20opposing%20forces%20birthing%20newness.%20Within%20that%20alchemy%2C%20more%20complex%2C%20imaginative%20truths%20emerge.%20For%20Alam%20and%20his%20team%2C%20the%20cancellation%20signals%20that%20voices%20from%20the%20Global%20South%20%E2%80%93%20the%20majority%20world%2C%20as%20Alam%20puts%20it%20%E2%80%93%20are%20not%20truly%20welcome%20beyond%20the%20region%20despite%20the%20lip%20service%20paid%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdiversity%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20repressions%20are%20in%20lockstep%20with%20a%20wider%20crackdown%20on%20expression.%20In%20the%20UK%2C%20Bristol%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-england-bristol-67496228%5C%22%3EArnolfini%20Gallery%20has%20dropped%20Palestinian%20events%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20fear%20they%20contradict%20state%20guidance%20that%20culture%20venues%20must%20remain%20apolitical%20or%20risk%20funding%20cuts.%20Given%20the%20political%20kernel%20of%20so%20much%20contemporary%20culture%2C%20this%20demand%20is%20absurd%20but%20it%20is%20indicative%20of%20Britain%E2%80%99s%20intolerant%20Tory%20administration.%20In%20truth%2C%20Arnolfini%20has%20held%20many%20political%20events%20so%20why%20do%20the%20Palestinian%20ones%20provoke%20censorship%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20is%20becoming%20Orwellian%20in%20its%20mechanisms%20of%20exclusion%2C%20erasure%20and%20silence.%20Even%20Jewish%20artists%2C%20such%20as%20Candice%20Breitz%2C%20are%20now%20being%20ostracised%20for%20their%20Palestinian%20sympathies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20anti-Semitism%20and%20there%20is%20Islamophobia%3A%20real%2C%20violent%20ideologies%20that%20destroy%20lives.%20There%20are%20also%20a%20million%20ghosts%2C%20fantasies%2C%20mis-speakings%20and%20mis-perceptions%20of%20those%20hate%20crimes.%20We%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20distinguish%20them.%20We%20need%20to%20understand%20who%20has%20the%20power%20to%20kill%20us%20and%20who%20is%20expressing%20an%20opinion%20with%20which%20we%20may%20not%20agree%20but%20which%20does%20not%20endanger%20us.%20Otherwise%2C%20we%20will%20waste%20our%20energy%20fighting%20shadows%20while%20the%20real%20monsters%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20argued%20that%20Weiwei%E2%80%99s%20tweet%20could%20be%20construed%20as%20anti-Semitic%2C%20my%20non-Jewish%20partner%20didn%E2%80%99t%20get%20it.%20I%20explained.%20He%20got%20it.%20Or%20said%20he%20did.%20That%E2%80%99s%20ok.%20That%E2%80%99s%20two%20people%20having%20different%20histories.%20(My%20partner%E2%80%99s%20Argentinian%20and%20objects%20every%20time%20I%20forget%20to%20describe%20those%20islands%20in%20the%20South%20Atlantic%20as%20Las%20Malvinas.)%20That%E2%80%99s%20all%20of%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20horror%20in%20Gaza%20is%20ripping%20faultlines%20through%20the%20art%20sector.%20The%20failure%20of%20major%20institutions%20to%20condemn%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20war%20crimes%20in%20Gaza%20as%20they%20condemned%20Putin%E2%80%99s%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20has%20triggered%20outrage%2C%20protests%20and%20sit-ins.%20Those%20who%20disagree%20say%20that%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20massacre%20makes%20such%20comparisons%20shaky.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETime%20and%20again%20I%20remember%20lines%20by%20the%20radical%20poet%20Adrienne%20Rich%2C%20who%20was%20Jewish%20on%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20side.%20%E2%80%9CSplit%20at%20the%20root%2FNeither%20Gentile%20nor%20Jew%20%5B%E2%80%A6but%5D%20I%E2%80%99m%20a%20good%20reader%20of%20histories.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20be%20superlative%20historians%20to%20recognise%2C%20as%20Ant%C3%B3nio%20Guterres%20said%2C%20that%20October%207%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.france24.com%2Fen%2Fvideo%2F20231024-hamas-attacks-did-not-happen-in-a-vacuum-guterres-says%5C%22%3Edidn%E2%80%99t%20happen%20in%20a%20vacuum%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Nor%20did%20the%20atrocities%20in%20Gaza.%20The%20ghosts%20of%20millions%20in%20Europe%20and%20Palestine%20haunt%20those%20dying%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20I%20condemn%20October%207%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20believe%20Palestinian%20people%20should%20pay%20for%20Hitler%E2%80%99s%20crimes.%20Art%20stakes%20itself%20on%20empathy%3A%20between%20artist%20and%20subject%3B%20art%20and%20viewer.%20It%20also%20wagers%20on%20mystery%3A%20that%20which%20bewilders%20us%2C%20makes%20us%20hesitate.%20Sometimes%20it%20makes%20us%20angry.%20Sometimes%20it%20redeems%20us.%20Sometimes%20it%20does%20both.%20It%E2%80%99s%20somewhere%20to%20backtrack%2C%20rethink%20then%20recomplicate.%20The%20lady%20who%20compared%20the%20Jews%20to%20Nazis%20had%2C%20as%20a%20young%20woman%2C%20hidden%20a%20Jew%20in%20her%20attic%20during%20the%20war%20at%20enormous%20personal%20risk.%20Humanity%20is%20as%20multi-faceted%20as%20a%20diamond.%20Art%20is%20a%20place%20where%20its%20strangeness%20can%20shine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cancellations%20damage%20the%20freedom%20and%20creativity%20they%20claim%20to%20protect.%20As%20James%20Baldwin%20put%20it%3A%20%E2%80%9CLife%20is%20more%20important%20than%20art.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20art%20is%20so%20important.%E2%80%9D%20If%20dialogue%20across%20difference%20is%20shut%20down%20in%20the%20house%20of%20culture%2C%20what%20hope%20remains%20elsewhere%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERachel%20Spence%20is%20a%20poet%20and%20arts%20writer.%20Her%20latest%20book%20is%20%3C%2Fem%3EVenice%20Unclocked%3Cem%3E%20(2022%2C%20Ivory%20Press).%20Her%20work%20has%20appeared%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3EFinancial%20Times%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3EHyperallergic%3Cem%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Art%20Newspaper%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701778558000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F30153449%2FACF098D3-6123-4B67-A2E4-DCA712B4.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fart-world-succumbing-pressure-ostracising-support-palestine%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20conflation%20of%20anti-Zionism%20with%20anti-Semitism%20is%20dangerous%20and%20the%20culture%20sector%20is%20cracking%20under%20its%20weight.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fart-world-succumbing-pressure-ostracising-suppor