2C%20Congress%20had%20wrested%20Karnataka%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20while%20other%20southern%20states%20are%20ruled%20by%20non-BJP%20parties%20including%20Tamil%20Nadu%20where%20Congress%20ally%20DMK%20is%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Mr%20Senthilkumar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20(BJP)%20cannot%20come%20to%20South%20India.%20You%20see%20all%20the%20results%20of%20what%20happens%20in%20Kerala%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Karnataka%20...%20we%20are%20very%20strong%20over%20there.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20not%20be%20surprised%20if%20you%20have%20an%20option%20of%20converting%20all%20these%20states%20into%20Union%20territories%20so%20that%20you%20can%20come%20into%20indirect%20power%20because%20you%20can%20never%20dream%20of%20setting%20foot%20over%20there%20and%20taking%20control%20of%20all%20the%20southern%20states.%26quot%3B%20In%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20state%20BJP%20chief%20K%20Annamalai%20condemned%20the%20%26quot%3Binsensitive%26quot%3B%20remarks%20of%20the%20MP%2C%20saying%20the%20level%20of%20the%20party's%20discourse%20is%20%26quot%3Bsinking%26quot%3B%20like%20Chennai%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Barrogance%26quot%3B%20of%20DMK%20will%20be%20the%20prime%20reason%20for%20its%20downfall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20calling%20our%20North%20Indian%20friends%20Pani%20Puri%20sellers%2C%20toilet%20constructors%2C%20etc.%2C%20I.N.D.I.%20Alliance%20DMK%20MP%2C%20makes%20Gaumutra%20Jibes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChennai%20is%20sinking%20due%20to%20the%20misgovernance%20of%20DMK%20%26amp%3B%20and%20so%20is%20their%20level%20of%20discourse%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20Parliament%2C%26quot%3B%20Annamalai%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20flood-like%20situation%20in%20the%20state%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20condemns%20this%20insensitive%20remark%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20sa