3EAdnam%20Sami%20said%20he%20hasn't%20yet%20seen%20the%20film%20but%20will%20always%20speak%20up%20in%20order%20to%20defend%20the%20right%20of%20a%20creative%20artist.%20Hence%2C%20he's%20come%20out%20in%20defence%20of%20'Animal'%20while%20taking%20examples%20of%20some%20classic%20movies%20and%20artists%20like%20Al%20Pacino..%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BFalse%2C%20Ill-Informed...%26quot%3B%3A%20Apollo%20Hospitals%20Rubbishes%20%26quot%3BCash%20For%20Kidneys%26quot%3B%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fapollo-hospitals%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApollo%20Hospitals%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20denied%20a%20media%20report%20claiming%20its%20flagship%20facility%20in%20Delhi%20-%20the%20Indraprastha%20Apollo%20Hospital%20-%20is%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20an%20international%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fapollo-kidney-racket%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bcash%20for%20kidneys%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20racket%20that%20sees%20poor%20people%20from%20Myanmar%20(formerly%20Burma)%20flown%20to%20the%20city%20to%20have%20their%20kidneys%20harvested%20in%20exchange%20for%20Rs%2080-90%20lakh%20(%C2%A32%2C700%20to%20%C2%A33%2C100)%20each.%20The%20illegally%20acquired%20organs%20are%20then%20sold%20to%20ailing%20rich%20patients%20from%20around%20the%20world%2C%20including%20the%20United%20Kingdom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20be%20clear%2C%20the%20Indraprastha%20Medical%20Corporation%20Ltd%20(the%20Indraprastha%20Hospital)%20complies%20with%20every%20legal%20and%20ethical%20requirement%20for%20transplant%20procedures%2C%20including%20guidelines%20by%20the%20government%20and%20our%20extensive%20internal%20processes%2C%20which%20exceed%20compliance%20requirements%2C%26quot%3B%20Apollo%20Hospitals%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20allegations%20made%20in%20the%20recent%20international%20media%20(report)%20against%20IMCL%20are%20absolutely%20false%2C%20ill-informed%2C%20and%20misleading.%20All%20the%20facts%20were%20shared%20in%20detail%20with%20the%20concerned%20journalist%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20hospital%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20multi-billion%20dollar%20Apollo%20Hospitals%20group%2C%20said%20in%20a%20report%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20IMCL%20spokesperson%20said%20every%20donor%20had%20to%20provide%20documentation%20from%20their%20government%20-%20which%20confirms%20a%20familial%20relationship%20to%20the%20recipient%20-%20and%20that%20a%20government-appointed%20committee%20at%20the%20hospital%20reviewed%20each%20case%2C%20and%20interviewed%20each%20donor%20and%20recipient%2C%20before%20allowing%20the%20transplant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20said%20IMCL%20then%20re-validates%20each%20document%20with%20the%20concerned%20embassy.%20The%20donor%20and%20recipient%20then%20undergo%20medical%20tests%20that%20would%20red-flag%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20genetic%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20steps%20far%20exceed%20any%20compliance%20requirements%20for%20a%20transplant%20procedure%20and%20ensure%20the%20donor%20and%20recipient%20are%20related%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said%2C%20stating%20IMCL%20is%20%26quot%3Bcommitted%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20ethical%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Heath%20Ministry%20has%20not%20yet%20commented%20on%20The%20Telegraph's%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApollo%20Hospitals%20also%20spoke%20to%20The%20Telegraph%20and%20declared%20itself%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20shocked%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20report.%20It%20said%20it%20would%20launch%20an%20internal%20investigation%2C%20and%20stressed%20that%20%26quot%3Bany%20suggestion%20of%20willful%20complicity%2C%20or%20implicit%20sanctioning%2C%20of%20any%20illegal%20activities%20relating%20to%20organ%20transplants%20is%20wholly%20denied%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fglobal-health%2Fscience-and-disease%2Fkidney-organ-trafficking-scandal-private-healthcare-india-myanmar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fa%3E%20report%2C%20published%209%20am%20Saturday%2C%20quotes%20an%20'agent'%20in%20the%20alleged%20illegal%20trade%20as%20suggesting%20the%20steps%20outlined%20may%20not%20be%20followed%20as%20strictly%20or%20as%20consistently%20as%20the%20hospital%20stated.%20%26quot%3BThe%20hospital%20asks%20the%20official%20questions....%20and%20on%20this%20side%20they%20tell%20the%20official%20lies%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20had%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'agent'%20told%20The%20Telegraph%20%26quot%3Bit%20is%20big%20business...%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20those%20involved%20%26quot%3Bwork%20together%20to%20get%20around%20obstacles%20between%20the%20two%20governments%26quot%3B%20since%20it%20is%20illegal%2C%20in%20India%20and%20Myanmar%2C%20to%20pay%20for%20or%20receive%20organs%20from%20a%20stranger%20without%20the%20authorities'%20permission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20The%20Telegraph%2C%20the%20racket%20involves%20extensive%20forgery%20-%20everything%20from%20'family'%20photographs%2C%20that%20suggest%20a%20relationship%20between%20the%20donor%20and%20recipient%2C%20to%20government%20documents%2C%20and%20that%20the%20money%20paid%20to%20the%20donor%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bthank%20you%26quot%3B%20payment%20and%20not%20for%20%26quot%3Bbuying%26quot%3B%20a%20kidney.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20allegations%20of%20an%20illegal%20organ%20racket%20have%20been%20made%20against%20Apollo%20Hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20Delhi%20Police%20questioned%20two%20senior%20doctors%20from%20the%20Indraprastha%20Hospital%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20kidney%20trading%20scam.%20This%20was%20after%20the%20arrest%20of%20a%20senior%20nephrologist's%20staff%20member%20and%20after%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkolkata-news%2Falleged-kingpin-of-apollo-kidney-racket-arrested-in-kolkata-1416563%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ET%20Rajkumar%20Rao%2C%20the%20alleged%20kingpin%20of%20the%20scam%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20also%20taken%20into%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fkidney-racket-busted-in-delhis-apollo-hospital-5-persons-arrested-1415359%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKidney%20Racket%20Busted%20In%20Delhi's%20Apollo%20Hospital%2C%205%20Persons%20Arrested%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Apollo%20Hospitals%20said%20it%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bvictim%20of%20a%20well-orchestrated%20operation%20carried%20out%20by%20few%20individuals%20with%20malafide%20intent%20(and)%20who%20deliberately%20committed%20forgery%20and%20fraud%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20hospital%20has%20the%20highest%20regard%20for%20the%20law...%20and%20urges%20police%20to%20take%20their%20investigation%20to%20its%20logical%20conclusion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20input%20from%20agencies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701776520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-06%2Fdelhi-apollo_650x400_61465032467.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fapollo-hospitals-the-telegraph-cash-for-kidneys-racket-false-ill-informed-apollo-hospitals-rubbishes-cash-for-kidneys-report-4635970%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Apollo%20Hospitals%20has%20denied%20a%20British%20media%20report%20claiming%20the%20Indraprastha%20Apollo%20Hospital%20in%20Delhi%20is%20at%2