20media.%20%26quot%3BHe%20(Mr%20Gogamedi)%20used%20to%20back%20our%20enemies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Is%20Rohit%20Godara%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGodara%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Bikaner's%20Lunakaran%2C%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20in%20Canada.%20He%20has%20over%2032%20cases%20registered%20against%20him%20at%20various%20police%20stations%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%2C%20Godara%20used%20to%20run%20extortion%20rackets%20against%20businessmen%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20demanding%20sums%20ranging%20from%20Rs%205%20crore%20to%20Rs%2017%20crore.%20He%20is%20also%20the%20main%20accused%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20gangster%20Raju%20Thehat%20in%20Sikar%20last%20year%20-%20a%20crime%20Godara%20took%20full%20responsibility%20for%20in%20a%20similar%20Facebook%20post%2C%20adding%20that%20Thehat%20was%20eliminated%20for%20the%20deaths%20of%20gangsters%20Anandpal%20Singh%20and%20Balveer%20Banuda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGodara%20is%20also%20one%20of%20the%20accused%20in%20the%20sensational%20murder%20of%20rapper%20Sidhu%20Moose%20Wala.%20The%20Punjabi%20rapper%20was%2028%20when%20he%20was%20shot%20dead%20in%20Punjab's%20Mansa%20district%20on%20May%2029%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2013%20last%20year%2C%20Godara%20fled%20New%20Delhi%20to%20Dubai%20on%20a%20fake%20passport%20using%20the%20name%20'Pawan%20Kumar'.%20There%20is%20an%20Interpol%20Red%20Notice%20circular%20issued%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Is%20Sukhdev%20Singh%20Gogamedi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGogamedi%20formed%20Shri%20Rashtriya%20Rajput%20Karni%20Sena%20-%20a%20different%20outfit%20than%20Shri%20Rajput%20Karni%20Sena%20that%20led%20protests%20against%20the%202018%20film%20'Padmaavat'%20-%20after%20he%20was%20expelled%20from%20Sri%20Rajput%20Karni%20Sena%20in%202015%20over%20differences%20with%20its%20founder%20Lokendra%20Singh%20Kalvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%2012%3A30%20pm%20today%2C%20Mr%20Gogamedi's%2