20where%20the%20party%20had%20previously%20won%20six%20out%20of%20eight%20seats%20in%202018.%20This%20time%2C%20Congress%20secured%20five%20out%20of%20eight%20seats%2C%20while%20one%20went%20to%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20and%20two%20to%20BJP.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20change%20in%20political%20dynamics%20since%20the%20last%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20initially%20came%20out%20with%20the%20slogan%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EKam%20Kiya%20Dil%20se%2C%20Gehlot%20Phir%20se%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%99%20which%20was%20later%20changed%20to%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EKam%20kiya%20dil%20se%2C%20Congress%20phir%20se%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%20as%20the%20party%20leadership%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20disappoint%20the%20Sachin%20Pilot%20camp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20this%20time%20the%20party%20failed%20to%20influence%20Gurjar%20votes%20in%20the%20state.%20Gurjars%2C%20Jats%2C%20Rajputs%2C%20and%20Meenas%20play%20key%20roles%20in%20forming%20the%20government.%20Gurjars%E2%80%99s%20anger%20is%20palpable%20over%20not%20handing%20over%20the%20reins%20to%20Pilot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20community%20holds%20influence%20over%20around%2030%20seats%2C%20mainly%20in%20the%20Karauli%2C%20Tonk%2C%20Hindaun%2C%20and%20Dausa%20districts%20of%20eastern%20Rajasthan.%20Out%20of%20the%2031%20seats%20that%20the%20Congress%20lost%20in%20the%20Rajasthan%20Assembly%20election%2C%2014%20come%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Felections%2Frajasthan-assembly%2Frajasthan-assembly-election-results-gujjar-disenchantment-costs-the-congress-dearly%2Farticle67602067.ece%5C%22%3Eeastern%20part%20of%20the%20state%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20Pilot%E2%80%99s%20community%2C%20the%20Gujjars%2C%20hold%20sway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigh-profile%20assembly%20seats%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmber%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Satish%20Poonia%2C%20a%20prominent%20Jat%20leader%20and%20former%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%2