%20in%20Rajasthan%20politics%2C%20Rajendra%20Rathore%2C%20was%20defeated%20from%20Taranagar%20by%20a%20margin%20of%2010%2C345%20votes%20to%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Narendra%20Budania.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Taranagar%20was%20the%20only%20place%20where%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20campaigned%20for%20Congress%20on%20November%2016%2C%20just%20eight%20days%20before%20the%20voting%20on%20November%2025%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20time%20of%20ticket%20distribution%2C%20the%20senior%20leadership%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20happy%20with%20Gehlot%E2%80%99s%20decisions%20and%20influence%20in%20ticket%20distribution%2C%20which%20later%20resulted%20in%20significant%20losses%20for%20the%20party.%20Despite%20this%2C%20candidates%20like%20Shanti%20Dhariwal%20from%20Kota-North%20managed%20to%20secure%20a%20place%20in%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha%2C%20even%20though%20senior%20leadership%20had%20questioned%20and%20alleged%20him%20as%20a%20corrupt%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20was%20largely%20absent%20from%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20in%20Rajasthan.%20Though%20he%20referred%20to%20Rajasthan%20government%20welfare%20schemes%20during%20his%20campaign%20in%20other%20states%2C%20he%20did%20not%20hold%20any%20roadshow.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701776115000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F22112200%2FF84a12kXkAAI7Ua.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fgehlot-pilot-rivalry-congress-drubbing-rajasthan%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20government%20appears%20to%20have%20received%20popular%20support%20for%20its%20welfare%20schemes%2C%20the%20Congress%20lost%20to%20the%20BJP%20due%20to%20its%20ineffective%20campaign%20strategy%20and%20poor%20selection%20of%20candidates.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fgehlot-pilot-rivalry-congress-drubbing-rajasthan%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3