99s%20concerns%20on%20jobs%2C%20land%2C%20identity%20etc.%2C%20but%20it%20is%20unlikely%20to%20concede%20to%20the%20statehood%20demand%20for%20the%20union%20territory%20carved%20out%20in%202019.%20These%20indications%20came%20after%20a%20high-powered%20committee%20headed%20by%20Union%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20home%20affairs%20Nitayanad%20Rai%20met%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20Tuesday%20to%20discuss%20the%20concerns%20and%20issues%20emerging%20in%20Ladakh%20since%20the%20August%202019%20decision%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20bifurcate%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20into%20two%20union%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMeeting%20and%20demands%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high-powered%20committee%2C%20which%20also%20includes%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20Apex%20Body%20Leh%20and%20Kargil%20Democratic%20Alliance%2C%20met%20in%20North%20Block%20on%20Tuesday%20after%20a%20gap%20of%20more%20than%20five%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meeting%2C%20the%20leaders%20from%20Leh%20and%20Kargil%20reiterated%20their%20four-point%20agenda%3A%20statehood%20for%20Ladakh%2C%20safeguards%20under%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%2C%20two%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20for%20the%20union%20territory%20and%20employment%20opportunities%20for%20the%20youth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20representatives%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20didn%E2%80%99t%20give%20any%20assurance%20on%20fulfilling%20these%20demands%2C%20but%20told%20the%20leadership%20of%20Ladakh%20that%20talks%20will%20continue%20to%20address%20concerns%20of%20the%20people%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20learnt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20is%20understood%20to%20have%20told%20the%20delegation%20that%20the%20government%20will%20look%20at%20options%20on%20how%20to%20address%20their%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Chering%20Dorjay%2C%20former%20minister%20and%20member%20of%20Apex%20Body%20Leh%2C%20said%20they%20raised%20the%20four%20-point%20agenda%20during%20the%20meeting.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20minister%20listened%20to%20our%20demands%2C%20but%20neither%20rejected%20them%20nor%20accepted%20them.%20He%20told%20us%20that%20they%20will%20hold%20another%20meeting%20to%20discuss%20these%20issues%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20about%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20the%20statehood%20demand%2C%20Dorjay%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20neither%20said%20yes%20nor%20no.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProminent%20political%20and%20social%20activist%20and%20member%20of%20the%20Kargil%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(KDA)%20Sajjad%20Kargili%20said%20that%20they%20told%20the%20Centre%20that%20these%20four%20demands%20should%20be%20met%20to%20fulfil%20the%20aspirations%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20told%20that%20the%20committee%20will%20meet%20again%20after%20the%20ongoing%20winter%20session%20is%20over%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CCold%E2%80%9D%20on%20statehood%20demand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20what%20could%20indicate%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20cold%20attitude%20towards%20the%20demand%20for%20statehood%2C%20an%20official%20handout%20released%20after%20the%20talks%20didn%E2%80%99t%20mention%20that%20the%20issue%20was%20raised%20by%20the%20Ladakhi%20delegation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20ABL%20and%20KDA%20members%20submitted%20various%20issues%20pertaining%20to%20protection%20of%20rights%20of%20Ladakh%20residents%2C%20fast%20track%20recruitment%20processes%2C%20strengthening%20of%20LAHDCs%2C%20Greater%20participation%20in%20the%20decision%20making%20etc.%2C%E2%80%9D%20reads%20the%20official%20handout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20said%20that%20New%20Delhi%20would%20continue%20talks%20with%20the%20ABL%20and%20KDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShri%20Rai%20said%20that%20the%20Government%20would%20continue%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20ABL%20and%20KDA%20and%20people%20of%20Ladakh%20for%20holistic%20and%20sustainable%20development%20of%20the%20UT%20of%20Ladakh%20on%20regular%20basis%2C%E2%80%9D%20reads%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20BJP%20MP%20from%20Ladakh%2C%20Jamyang%20Tsering%20Namgayal%2C%20has%20pushed%20for%20constitutional%20safeguards%20beyond%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20for%20safeguarding%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20identity%20and%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20firmly%20advocate%20the%20necessity%20for%20constitutional%20safeguards%20exceeding%20the%20provisions%20laid%20down%20in%20the%206th%20schedule%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20specifically%20tailored%20to%20safeguard%20the%20interests%20and%20aspirations%20of%20tribal%20people%20of%20Ladakh%2C%E2%80%9D%20reads%20the%20MP%E2%80%99s%20letter%20to%20the%20MoS%20home%20affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%2C%20the%20autonomous%20district%20councils%20have%20specific%20legislative%2C%20executive%2C%20judicial%20and%20financial%20powers%20in%20the%20tribal%20areas%20of%20Meghalaya%2C%20Tripura%2C%20Mizoram%20and%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20such%20district%20has%20a%20council%2C%20which%20can%20make%20laws%20on%20certain%20specified%20matters%20like%20land%2C%20forests%2C%20canal%20water%2C%20shifting%20cultivation%2C%20village%20administration%2C%20inheritance%20of%20property%2C%20marriage%20and%20divorce%2C%20social%20customs%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20demand%20for%20Sixth%20Schedule%20implementation%20has%20become%20a%20rallying%20cry%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20especially%20in%20Buddhist-majority%20Leh%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Leh%20district%20had%20welcomed%20UT%20status%20for%20Ladakh%20in%202019%2C%20Muslim-majority%20Kargil%20district%20had%20opposed%20it%20and%20observed%20a%20shutdown%20for%20several%20weeks%20to%20show%20its%20anger%20over%20the%20%E2%80%9Cunilateral%E2%80%9D%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20leadership%20of%20both%20Leh%20and%20Kargil%20joined%20hands%20and%20decided%20to%20fight%20collectively%20for%20statehood%2C%20constitutional%20safeguards%20under%20the%20Sixth%20schedule%2C%20two%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20and%20employment%20for%20youth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20anger%20and%20discontent%20in%20the%20region%2C%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20in%20January%20this%20year%20announced%20a%20high-powered%20committee%20headed%20by%20Rai%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdiscuss%20measures%20to%20protect%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20unique%20culture%20and%20language%20taking%20into%20consideration%20its%20geographical%20location%20and%20its%20strategic%20importance%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20constitution%20of%20the%20committee%20faced%20criticism%20from%20both%20the%20conglomerates%20fighting%20for%20statehood%20and%20safeguards%20of%20Ladakh%2C%20saying%20that%20it%20not%20been%20mandated%20to%20discuss%20the%20demands%20raised%20by%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MHA%20reconstituted%20the%20committee%20and%20modified%20its%20terms%20of%20reference.%20Its%20terms%20of%20reference%20now%20includes%20examining%20constitutional%20safeguards%20that%20could%20be%20implemented%20to%20ensure%20the%20protections%20for%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFactors%20behind%20talks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20widely%20believed%20that%20geopolitical%20considerations%20and%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20own%20electoral%20exigencies%20are%20driving%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20talks%20with%20the%20leadership%20in%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocated%20on%20the%20ancient%20silk%20route%2C%20Ladakh%20has%20geopolitical%20importance%20as%20it%20shares%20borders%20with%20Pakistan%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20BJP%20would%20also%20like%20to%20see%20a%20resolution%20of%20these%20issues%20before%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20as%20it%20is%20keen%20to%20retain%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20parliament%20seat%20for%20the%20third%20connective%20term.%20These%20identity%20issues%20have%20put%20the%20party%20in%20a%20tight%20spot%20as%20its%20seat%20tally%20decreased%20in%20the%20Hill%20Council%20election%20held%20in%20Leh%20in%202020.%20In%20the%20recently%20held%20Hill%20Council%20election%20held%20in%20neighbouring%20Kargil%20district%2C%20it%20managed%20to%20win%20only%20two%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20National%20Conference-%20Congress%20alliance%20swept%20the%20polls%20by%20winning%2022%20out%20of%2026%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701775831000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F09125711%2Fvarun-nambiar-3SzqHcQ4eY0-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fladakh-leaders-statehood-demand-gets-a-cold-shoulder-from-the-union-government%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22However%2C%20the%20Centre%20is%20likely%20to%20assent%20to%20other%20demands%20over%20jobs%2C%20land%20and%20identity-related%20rights.%20Talks%20will%20resume%20after%20the%20winter%20session%20of%20parliament.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fladakh-leaders-statehood-demand-gets-a-cold-shoulder-from-the-union-government%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Wipro%20Consumer%20acquires%203%20brands%20from%20VVF%20to%20expand%20personal%20care%20segment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701775235000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-08%2F27%2Ffull%2F1693133194-2389.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fwipro-consumer-acquires-3-brands-from-vvf-to-expand-personal-care-segment-123120500682_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20acquisition%20will%20be%20a%20strategic%20expansion%20for%20Wipro%20in%20the%20personal%20wash%20segment%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0