0role%20of%20the%20SRC%20has%20to%20be%20strengthened%2C%20and%20members%20have%20to%20take%20a%20more%20active%20interest%20in%20its%20workings.%20Expanding%20the%20responsibilities%20of%20the%20SRC%20will%20enhance%20its%20importance%20within%20the%20board%20and%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20private%20sector%20banks%2C%20the%20SRCs%20have%20failed%20to%20protect%20the%20interests%20of%20employees%2C%20as%20seen%20in%20the%20high%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhemindrahazari.com%2F2023%2F09%2F05%2Findusind-bank-when-half-the-staff-left-why-didnt-independent-directors-think-it-worth-mentioning%2F%5C%22%3Eattrition%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%2031%25%20to%2051%25%20in%20some%20of%20the%20banks%20in%20FY23.%20This%20concern%20has%20prompted%20the%20RBI%20to%20publicly%20express%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbctv18.com%2Fbusiness%2Fcompanies%2Frbi-closely-watching-high-attrition-at-some-private-banks-says-shaktikanta-das-18207931.htm%5C%22%3Eits%20apprehensions.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20SRCs%20need%20to%20be%20activated%2C%20and%20have%20to%20take%20cognizance%20of%20material%20information%20that%20is%20brought%20to%20their%20knowledge%2C%20including%20non-public%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20engaging%20and%20being%20receptive%20to%20stakeholders%2C%20the%20SRCs%20can%20adopt%20a%20forward-looking%20approach.%20To%20operate%20successfully%2C%20the%20SRCs%20would%20need%20to%20be%20more%20proactive%20and%20engage%20with%20employee%20representatives%2C%20which%20is%20difficult%20in%20many%20private%20sector%20banks%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20staff%20unions%20and%20officer%20associations.%20Seeking%20advice%20from%20proxy%20advisory%20firms%20and%20even%20analysts%20covering%20the%20concerned%20companies%20may%20be%20crucial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rejection%20of%20the%20renewal%20of%20the%20term%20of%20an%20independent%20director%20by%20IndusInd%20Bank%20shareholders%2C%20despite%20it%20being%20supported%20by%20the%20founder%20and%20the%20board%2C%20is%20a%20major%20embarrassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20the%20renewal%20complied%20with%20regulatory%20norms%2C%20the%20rejection%20highlights%20the%20board%E2%80%99s%20lack%20of%20concern%20for%20current%20governance%20norms%2C%20and%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20SRC%20in%20briefing%20the%20board%20regarding%20the%20concerns%20of%20proxy%20advisory%20firms.%20Company%20boards%20have%20an%20organisational%20structure%2C%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20SRC%2C%20to%20address%20these%20issues%2C%20but%20this%20structure%20needs%20to%20be%20activated%20in%20order%20to%20improve%20governance%20in%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EHemindra%20Hazari%20is%20a%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20registered%20independent%20research%20analyst%3C%2Fi%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDISCLOSURE%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-attr%3D%5C%22not-done%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI%2C%20Hemindra%20Hazari%2C%20am%20a%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20registered%20independent%20research%20analyst%20(Regd.%20No.%20INH000000594).%20%3Cstrong%3EI%20own%20equity%20shares%20in%20all%20the%20companies%20mentioned%20in%20this%20report%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%3Cstrong%3EHDFC%20Bank%20subscribes%20to%20this%20analyst%E2%80%99s%20research%20and%20a%20member%20of%20this%20analyst%E2%80%99s%20family%20is%20employed%20with%20the%20bank%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20Views%20expressed%20in%20this%20Insight%20accurately%20reflect%20my%20personal%20opinion%20about%20the%20referenced%20securities%20and%20issuers%20and%2For%20other%20subject%20matter%20as%20appropriate.%20This%20Insight%20does%20not%20contain%20and%20is%20not%20based%20on%20any%20non-public%2C%20material%20information.%20To%20the%20best%20of%20my%20knowledge%2C%20the%20views%20expressed%20in%20this%20Insight%20comply%20with%20Indian%20law%20as%20well%20as%20applicable%20law%20in%20the%20country%20from%20which%20it%20is%20posted.%20I%20have%20not%20