%20and%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%3F%20To%20answer%20this%20critical%20question%2C%20we%20analyse%20the%20mistakes%20Congress%20made%20in%20the%20recent%20state%20elections%20as%20well%20as%20the%20strengths%20and%20strategies%20that%20benefitted%20BJP.%20The%20critical%20question%20facing%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20the%20core%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20is%3A%20what%20is%20its%20aim%20in%202024%3F%20To%20maximise%20the%20number%20of%20seats%20it%20can%20win%20or%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP%3F%20The%20answer%20could%20determine%20what%20happens%20in%20five%20months%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FnXiYo-FlLKg%3Fsi%3Dnclpeb_1tXvOzkV5%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701762600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fimg.youtube.com%2Fvi%2FnXiYo-FlLKg%2F0.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwatch-after-sunday-is-a-2024-modi-victory-or-is-it-too-early-to-write-off-the-opposition%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20critical%20question%20facing%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20the%20core%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20is%3A%20what%20is%20its%20aim%20in%202024%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwatch-after-sunday-is-a-2024-modi-victory-or-is-it-too-early-to-write-off-the-opposition%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mizoram%20Election%20Results%20Usher%20in%20New%20Politics%20and%20Developmental%20Challenges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F05131251%2FFKNdrT2VEAM9zbg.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAizawl%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20election%20results%20for%20the%20ninth%20Mizoram%20assembly%20elections%20are%20of%20great%20significance%20for%20the%20state.%20In%20the%20electoral%20history%20of%20the%20northeastern%20state%2C%20there%20has%20never%20been%20a%20situation%20where%20a%20mandate%20was%20for%20a%20hung%20assembly%20or%20for%20a%20coalition%20government.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20the%2035-year-old%20tradition%20of%20a%20government%20being%20formed%20either%20by%20the%20Congress%20or%20the%20regional%20Mizo%20National%20Front%20(MNF)%20has%20come%20to%20a%20close.%20A%20new%20and%20a%20third%20political%20party%20has%20been%20given%20a%20clear%20mandate%20to%20form%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20six-year-old%20Zoram%20People%E2%80%99s%20Movement%20(ZPM)%20has%20been%20given%20a%20huge%20mandate%20by%20the%20voters.%20In%20the%202018%20assembly%20elections%2C%20though%20the%20ZPM%20was%20attracting%20people%E2%80%99s%20attention%20as%20a%20new%20party%2C%20it%20could%20win%20only%20six%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20MNF%20stole%20the%20show%20with%2027%20seats.%20The%20scenario%20has%20changed%20these%20elections%20%E2%80%93%20it%20is%20the%20ZPM%20that%20won%2027%20seats%2C%20leaving%20the%20MNF%20with%20just%20ten%20seats.%20C.%20Ngunlianchunga%20has%20won%20the%20only%20seat%20for%20the%20Congress%20in%20Lawngtlai%20West%20Rural%3B%20he%20has%20won%20that%20seat%20for%20the%20third%20consecutive%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20the%20Congress%20presence%20in%20the%2040-member%20assembly%20has%20shrunk%20to%20one%20from%20five%2C%20the%20BJP%20could%20increase%20its%20tally%20in%20the%20state%20for%20the%20first%20time%20with%20two%20wins.%20This%2C%20when%20the%20Congress%20had%2020.82%25%20votes%20and%20BJP%20only%205.06%25%20votes.%20Still%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20seats%20won%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20become%20the%20third%20largest%20party%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20leaving%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20third%20position%20only%20in%20terms%20of%20vote%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20ZPM%20got%2037.86%25%20of%20the%20votes%20polled%2C%20MNF%20got%2035.10%25.%20The%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20which%20also%20tried%20its%20luck%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20along%20with%20NOTA%20and%20independents%20got%20a%20total%20of%201.14%25%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20also%20significant%20about%20these%20election%20results%20is%2C%20three%20women%20MLAs%20were%20elected%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20border%20state.%20While%20two%20of%20them%20belong%20to%20the%20ZPM%20(Lalrinpuii%20from%20the%20Lunglei%20East%20seat%20and%20Baryl%20Wenneihsangi%20from%20Aizawl%20South-3%20seat)%2C%20Prova%20Chakma%20of%20the%20MNF%20bagged%20the%20Tuipui%20West%20seat.%20While%20Prova%20Chakma%20defeated%20a%20BJP%20candidate%20to%20become%20the%20first%20woman%20MLA%20from%20the%20Chakma%20community%2C%20Baryl%20Venneihsangi%2C%20a%20popular%20news%20anchor%2C%20defeated%20an%20MNF%20candidate%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member.%20In%202014%2C%20a%20Congresswoman%20had%20won%20a%20by-election%20and%20entered%20the%20assembly%20after%2027%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20another%20noteworthy%20fact%20from%20the%20poll%20results%20is%20the%20loss%20of%20a%20sitting%20chief%20minister%2C%20Zoramthanga%20of%20MNF.%20However%2C%20if%20you%20look%20at%20Mizoram%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20history%2C%20whenever%20a%20ruling%20party%20loses%20elections%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20is%20defeated%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20needs%20highlighting%20is%20also%20this%3A%20while%20the%20ZPM%20had%20a%20good%20show%20mostly%20in%20the%20urban%20pockets%20%E2%80%93%20it%20won%20all%20the%2012%20seats%20in%20Aizawl%20City%2C%20four%20in%20Lunglei%20and%20all%20three%20in%20Serchhip%20%E2%80%93%20the%20MNF%20won%20all%2010%20seats%20in%20the%20rural%20areas.%20The%20BJP%20has%20won%20one%20seat%20from%20the%20Chakma%20region.%20The%20Congress%20and%20BJP%C2%A0have%20won%20seats%20in%20Saiha%20and%20Lawngtlai%20districts%20of%20south%20Mizoram.%20BJP%20has%20won%20two%20seats%20in%C2%A0Saiha%20district%20and%20Congress%20has%20won%20one%20of%20the%20two%20seats%20in%20Lawngtlai%20district.%20BJP%20has%20won%20both%C2%A0the%20seats%20of%20the%20Mara%20tribal%20community%20and%20Congress%20has%20won%20one%20seat%20from%20the%20Lai%20tribal%20community%20area%20of%20Lawngtlai%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20specificities%2C%20these%20elections%20are%20important%20for%20the%20main%20political%20players%20of%20the%20state%20in%20many%20ways.%20The%20ruling%20party%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20able%20to%20return%20to%20power.%20The%20ZPM%20created%20important%20history%20in%20the%20politics%20of%20Mizoram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20polls%20also%20registered%20a%20big%20fall%20for%20the%20Congress%20and%20a%20big%20rise%20for%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImpact%20on%20political%20leaders%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20significant%20question%20is%2C%20how%20will%20this%20election%20impact%20Zoramthanga%E2%80%99s%20supremacy%20within%20the%20MNF%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20ZPM%2C%20it%20will%20be%20challenging%20for%20Lalduhoma%20to%20keep%20together%20the%20two%20factions%20of%20ex-Congress%20and%20ex-MNF%20leaders%20who%20had%20shifted%20to%20his%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Congress%2C%20post%20its%20poor%20show%2C%20the%20leadership%20of%20state%20president%20Lalsawta%20will%20likely%20face%20a%20serious%20challenge%20from%20the%20supporters%20of%20the%20former%20chief%20minister%20Lalthanhawla%20within%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20questions%20thrown%20up%20by%20the%20December%204%20results%20have%20made%20this%20election%20important%20for%20politicians%20in%20many%20ways.%20Lalduhoma%E2%80%99s%20long%20wait%20for%20the%20political%20limelight%20is%20finally%20over%3B%20he%20had%20been%20waiting%20for%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20chair%20for%20the%20longest%20time%20in%20the%20state.%20If%20the%20ZPM%20was%20not%20to%20win%20this%20time%20around%2C%20Lalduhoma%E2%80%99s%20political%20future%20would%20likely%20have%20been%20eclipsed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Lalduhoma%20is%20set%20to%20rise%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20political%20innings%20of%20MNF%20supremo%20Zoramthanga%20have%20most%20likely%20come%20to%20an%20end.%20It%20is%20unlikely%20that%20he%20will%20fight%20another%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20BJP%2C%20due%20to%20the%20defeat%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20new%20leader%20Lalrinliana%20Sailo%20in%20these%20elections%2C%20his%20future%20in%20the%20party%20has%20become%20uncertain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWorking%20with%20the%20BJP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZPM%20leader%20and%20chief%20ministererial%20candidate%20Lalduhoma%2C%20while%20talking%20to%20the%20media%20after%20winning%20the%20elections%20on%20December%204%2C%20said%20that%20zero%20tolerance%20on%20state%20corruption%2C%20bringing%20about%20financial%20reforms%2C%20balanced%20development%20in%20the%20state%2C%20investigation%20of%20corruption%20cases%20by%20the%20CBI%20and%20engaging%20with%20the%20issue%20of%20Zo-unification%20(with%20the%20Kukis%20and%20Maras%20of%20neighbouring%20Manipur)%20are%20going%20to%20be%20the%20main%20priorities%20of%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalduhoma%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20challenge%20will%20be%20to%20fulfil%20the%20big%20promises%20ZPM%20had%20made%20to%20the%20voters%2C%20including%20on%20the%20Zo-unification%20issue.%20One%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20for%20the%20new%20government%20will%20also%20be%20to%20bring%20financial%20mismanagement%20under%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ZPM%20is%20likely%20to%20join%20the%20BJP-led%20North%20East%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NEDA)%20and%20the%20NDA%2C%20as%20Mizoram%20is%20dependent%20on%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%20for%20its%20economic%20needs.%20And%20there%20could%20be%20more%20to%20it%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20it%20has%20won%20handsomely%20to%20form%20a%20government%20on%20its%20own%2C%20the%20ZPM%20is%20already%20under%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20from%20the%20BJP%20to%20induct%20at%20least%20one%20of%20its%20MLAs%20into%20the%20new%20government.%20If%20a%20regional%20party%20runs%20a%20state%20government%2C%20it%20has%20to%20somewhat%20compromise%20to%20establish%20some%20sort%20of%20harmony%20and%20working%20relations%20with%20the%20ruling%20party%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20particularly%20so%20when%20it%20is%20financially%20dependent%20on%20it.%20Along%20with%20its%20Christian%20politics%2C%20ZPM%20will%20also%20then%20have%20to%20maintain%20an%20equilibrium%20of%20sorts%20with%20the%20Hindutva%20politics%20of%20the%20BJP.%20Church%20organisations%20have%20influence%20on%20the%20politics%20of%20Mizoram.%20The%20two%20BJP%20MLAs%20from%20the%20Mara%20community%2C%20who%20are%20Christian%20too%2C%20will%20also%20then%20face%20the%20challenge%20of%20forging%20a%20rapport%20with%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindutva%20ideology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20times%20to%20come%2C%20it%20will%20be%20seen%20how%20this%20working%20relationship%20of%20the%20ZPM%20in%20general%20with%20the%20BJP%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20and%20the%20Mara%20MLAs%20in%20particular%20with%20the%20national%20party%2C%20will%20pan%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESuwa%20Lal%20Jangu%20is%20assistant%20professor%20of%20political%20science%2C%20Mizoram%20University%2C%20Aizawl.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701762266000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F05131251%2FFKNdrT2VEAM9zbg.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmizoram-election-results-usher-in-new-politics-and-developmental-challenges%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20break%20from%20history%2C%20the%20six-year-old%20Zoram%20People%E2%80%99s%20Movement%20has%20been%20given%20a%20huge%20mandate%20by%20the%20voters.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmizoram-election-results-usher-in-new-politics-and-developmental-challenges%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22YouTuber%20Trevor%20Jacob%20jailed%20after%20crashing%20plane%20for%20views%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701761571000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F157FC%2Fproduction%2F_129706088_trevorplane.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67622247%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trevor%20Jacob%20is%20sentenced%20to%20six%20months%20in%20prison%20for%20staging%20a%20plane%20crash%20for%20social%20media%20clicks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A304%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67622247%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67622247.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67622247.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Suhana%20complained%20about%20Ganesh%20Hegde%20to%20SRK%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701761126000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105748908%2Cimgsize-19370.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fheres-how-shah-rukh-khan-reacted-when-suhana-khan-complained-about-ganesh-hegde-to-him%2Farticleshow%2F105748908.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105748908.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20choreographer%20spoke%20about%20the%20dance%20forms%20in%20'The%20Archies'%20and%20shared%20his%20experience%20of%20working%20with%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20and%20his%20daughter%20Suhana%20Khan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fheres-how-shah-rukh-khan-reacted-when-suhana-khan-complained-about-ganesh-hegde-to-him%2Farticleshow%2F105748908.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Protect%20Sikhs%20in%20America'%3A%20US%20Community%20Groups%20Demand%20Transparency%20on%20'Pannun%20Plot'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F26162627%2Fsandy-millar-UfY8CbyIwRg-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20handful%20of%20US-based%20Sikh%20community%20organisations%20have%20demanded%20that%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20be%20fully%20transparent%20about%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20alleged%20Indian%20%E2%80%98plot%E2%80%99%20to%20kill%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20apart%20from%20asking%20other%20groups%20to%20begin%20conversations%20%E2%80%9Cabout%20authoritarianism%20and%20human%20rights%20in%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELed%20by%20the%20group%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jakara.org%2Fprotectsikhs%5C%22%3EJakara%20Movement%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20issued%20a%20list%20of%20demands%20after%20it%20was%20revealed%20last%20week%20that%20an%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fpannun-assassination-plot-india-enquiry-committee-set-up%5C%22%3Eidentified%20Indian%20government%20employee%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%20had%20directed%20the%20thwarted%20plot%20to%20target%20an%20American%20Sikh%20who%20is%20active%20in%20the%20Khalistan%20movement.%20Jaraka%20Movement%20said%20that%20all%20Americans%20and%20people%20committed%20to%20democratic%20principles%20should%20%E2%80%9Ccome%20forward%20to%20ensure%20that%20Sikhs%20and%20all%20Indian%20minority%20communities%20living%20in%20the%20US%20are%20safe%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20transnational%20repression.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20also%20highlighted%20the%20alleged%20Indian%20involvement%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20a%20Canadian%20Sikh%20citizen%2C%20in%20Vancouver%20in%20June.%20Jakara%20Movement%20recounted%20that%20the%20FBI%20had%20warned%20several%20other%20Sikhs%20in%20the%20US%20a%20few%20months%20ago%20that%20their%20lives%20could%20be%20in%20danger%20as%20well.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20has%20been%20at%20least%20one%20documented%20instance%20in%20recent%20months%20of%20an%20Indian%20government%20operative%20surveilling%20a%20Sikh%20house%20of%20worship%20in%20the%20US%20and%20then%20demanding%20information%20from%20a%20religious%20leader%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSikhs%20and%20all%20Americans%20living%20in%20the%20U.S.%20should%20be%20able%20to%20practice%20their%20constitutional%20and%20human%20rights%20without%20experiencing%20repression%20from%20a%20foreign%20power.%20They%20must%20be%20able%20to%20gather%2C%20protest%20and%20speak%20out%2C%20free%20from%20intimidation%2C%20harassment%2C%20surveillance%20and%20violence%20from%20other%20nations%20and%20their%20agents%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sikh%20groups%20requested%20all%20democratic%20organisations%20and%20citizens%20to%20build%20pressure%20on%20the%20US%20government%2C%20suggesting%20the%20following%20steps%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Express%20solidarity%20with%20the%20Sikh%20community%20and%20other%20affected%20Indian%20minority%20communities%20in%20the%20US%20through%20statements%2C%20letters%20and%20online%20posts%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Convene%20conversations%20about%20authoritarianism%20and%20human%20rights%20in%20India%20at%20schools%2C%20colleges%2C%20libraries%20and%20other%20centers%20featuring%20impacted%20communities%2C%20activists%20and%20scholars%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20Demand%20the%20DOJ%20be%20fully%20transparent%20about%20the%20investigation%2C%20unseal%20all%20indictments%20and%20prosecute%20all%20those%20responsible%20no%20matter%20how%20senior%20their%20position%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20Demand%20the%20US%20government%20sanction%20any%20individuals%20and%20entities%20employed%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%20found%20to%20be%20responsible%20or%20connected%20to%20the%20foiled%20plot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20Call%20on%20state%20legislative%20bodies%20and%20Congress%20to%20hold%20hearings%20on%20transnational%20repression%20that%20include%20discussion%20of%20India%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E6.%20Call%20on%20Congress%20to%20pass%20and%20President%20Biden%20to%20sign%20the%20Transnational%20Repression%20Policy%20Act%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E7.%20Urge%20the%20US%20to%20honor%20its%20commitments%20as%20a%20signatory%20to%20the%20Declaration%20of%20Principles%20to%20Combat%20Transnational%20Repression%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E8.%20Urge%20the%20US%20and%20other%20democracies%20to%20better%20coordinate%20on%20combating%20transnational%20repression%2C%20including%20imposing%20penalties%20like%20sanctions%2C%20diplomatic%20expulsions%20and%20criminal%20charges%3B%20and%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E9.%20Insist%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%20cooperate%20fully%20with%20all%20investigations.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701759922000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F26162627%2Fsandy-millar-UfY8CbyIwRg-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fsikhs-america-community-groups-transparency-pannun-plot%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20groups%20issued%20a%20series%20of%20suggestions%20to%20build%20pressure%2C%20including%20calling%20on%20state%20legislative%20bodies%20and%20Congress%20to%20hold%20hearings%20on%20%26quot%3Btransnational%20repression%20that%20include%20discussion%20of%20India%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fsikhs-america-community-groups-transparency-pannun-plot%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Magnitude%205.1%20earthquake%20f