w-1235821584%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vivek%20Ramaswamy%2C%20Nikki%20Haley%3A%204%20Republicans%20To%20Lock%20Horns%20At%20Dec%206%20Debate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20stage%20is%20set%20for%20the%20fourth%20Republican%20debate%20where%20the%20remaining%20four%20presidential%20hopefuls%20will%20engage%20in%20what's%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20heated%20exchange%20of%20views%20and%20barbs.%20The%20debate%20is%20scheduled%20to%20take%20place%20at%20the%20Moody%20Music%20Hall%2C%20University%20of%20Alabama%2C%20in%20Tuscaloosa.%20The%20Republican%20National%20Committee%20(RNC)%20has%20established%20stringent%20qualification%20criteria%20for%20candidates%20to%20secure%20a%20spot%20in%20this%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFlorida%20Governor%20Ron%20DeSantis%2C%20former%20South%20Carolina%20Governor%20Nikki%20Haley%2C%20entrepreneur%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%2C%20and%20former%20New%20Jersey%20Governor%20Chris%20Christie%20will%20take%20part%20in%20the%20debate%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20December%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERon%20DeSantis%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20considered%20the%20man%20most%20likely%20to%20take%20on%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20Ron%20DeSantis%20now%20finds%20himself%20in%20a%20competitive%20race%20for%20second%20place.%20He%20is%20reportedly%20also%20dealing%20with%20issues%20within%20his%20campaign%20team%20but%20despite%20that%2C%20he%20has%20completed%20the%20goal%20of%20holding%20events%20in%2099%20counties%20in%20Iowa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENikki%20Haley%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENikki%20Haley%20has%20been%20getting%20more%20attention%20lately%2C%20especially%20since%20the%20campaign%20is%20now%20focusing%20on%20foreign%20policy%20after%20the%20surprise%20attack%20on%20Israel%20by%20Hamas.%20With%20Tim%20Scott%20dropping%20out%20of%20the%20race%2C%20Haley%20is%20getting%20more%20support%20from%20wealthy%20donors%20and%20Wall%20Street.%20Americans%20for%20Prosperity%2C%20a%20big%20advocacy%20group%2C%20recently%20endorsed%20her.%20She's%20also%20solidly%20holding%20the%20second%20spot%20in%20New%20Hampshire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVivek%20Ramaswamy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiotech%20entrepreneur%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20hasn't%20gained%20much%20support%20in%20the%20polls.%20He%20has%20had%20a%20hard%20time%20standing%20out%20from%20the%20former%20President%2C%20and%20his%20political%20director%20recently%20switched%20to%20join%20Trump's%20campaign.%20Despite%20ongoing%20criticism%20of%20elected%20Republicans%2C%20promises%20to%20cut%20government%20jobs%2C%20and%20warnings%20about%20preventing%20World%20War%20III%2C%20Ramaswamy%20is%20trying%20some%20new%20strategies.%20After%20running%20an%20unconventional%20campaign%2C%20he%20is%20now%20doing%20more%20traditional%20things%20like%20setting%20up%20a%20campaign%20office%20in%20Iowa%20and%20spending%20a%20lot%20on%20TV%20ads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChris%20Christie%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20New%20Jersey%20Governor%20Chris%20Christie%2C%20positioning%20his%20campaign%20in%20opposition%20to%20Trump%2C%20is%20facing%20challenges%20as%20he%20trails%20behind%20competitors%20in%20national%20and%20Iowa%20polls.%20Even%20though%20he%20has%20performed%20better%20in%20New%20Hampshire%2C%20many%20Republicans%20suggest%20he%20drop%20out%2C%20especially%20as%20the%20anti-Trump%20group%20in%20the%20party%20rallies%20around%20candidates%20like%20Nikki%20Haley%20or%20Ron%20DeSantis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20Christie%20has%20expressed%20his%20intention%20to%20persist%20with%20his%20campaign%20until%20the%20Republican%20convention%20next%20summer.%20However%2C%20he%20also%20mentioned%20the%20possibility%20of%20reconsidering%20his%20candidacy%20if%20he%20performs%20poorly%20in%20the%20Granite%20State.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20who%20is%20leading%20in%20the%20race%20for%20the%20GOP%20nomination%2C%20won't%20be%20participating%20in%20the%20event.%20Instead%2C%20he%20will%20be%20in%20Florida%2C%20attending%20a%20fundraiser%20for%20a%20super%20PAC%20that%20supports%20his%20candidacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20eligible%20for%20the%20fourth%20debate%2C%20candidates%20were%20required%20to%20attain%20a%20minimum%20of%206%25%20support%20in%20two%20national%20polls%20or%206%25%20in%20one%20national%20poll%2C%20coupled%20with%20two%20polls%20from%20a%20selection%20of%20early-voting%20states%2C%20namely%20Iowa%2C%20New%20Hampshire%2C%20Nevada%2C%20and%20South%20Carolina.%20The%20RNC%20approved%20all%20qualifying%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701757380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fj8dkan9o_vivek-ramaswamy-1200_625x300_13_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvivek-ramaswamy-nikki-haley-4-republicans-to-lock-horns-at-dec-6-debate-4634753%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20stage%20is%20set%20for%20the%20fourth%20Republican%20debate%20where%20the%20remaining%20four%20presidential%20hopefuls%20will%20engage%20in%20what's%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20heated%20exchange%20of%20views%20and%20barbs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvivek-ramaswamy-nikki-haley-4-republicans-to-lock-horns-at-dec-6-debate-4634753%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvivek-ramaswamy-nikki-haley-4-republicans-to-lock-horns-at-dec-6-debate-4634753%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvivek-ramaswamy-nikki-haley-4-republicans-to-lock-horns-at-dec-6-debate-4634753%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Banks%20Write%20Off%20Rs%2010.6%20Lakh%20Crore%20in%205%20Years%2C%20Mostly%20Linked%20to%20Large%20Corporates%3A%20Govt%20Data%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F16101457%2Frupee-gb36195718_1920.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20government%20on%20Monday%2C%20December%204%2C%20informed%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20that%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20Scheduled%20Commercial%20Banks%20(SCBs)%20wrote%20off%20nearly%20Rs%2010.6%20lakh%20crore%2C%20with%20almost%20half%20of%20this%20amount%20belonging%20to%20large%20industrial%20houses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApproximately%202%2C300%20borrowers%2C%20each%20with%20loans%20exceeding%20Rs%205%20crore%2C%20deliberately%20defaulted%20on%20around%20Rs%202%20lakh%20crore%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Feconomy%2Findian-banks-write-off-106-lakh-crore-in-5-years-50-linked-to-large-corporates%2Farticle67604297.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHindu%20BusinessLine%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20write-offs%2C%20conducted%20in%20accordance%20with%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20guidelines%20and%20approved%20bank%20board%20policies%2C%20involve%20removing%20non-performing%20assets%20(NPAs)%20from%20balance%20sheets%20after%20full%20provisioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSuch%20write-offs%20do%20not%20result%20in%20waiver%20of%20liabilities%20of%20borrowers%20to%20repay%2C%E2%80%9D%20Minister%20of%20State%20in%20the%20Finance%20Ministry%20Bhagwat%20Karad%20said%20in%20a%20written%20response.%20The%20process%20of%20recovery%20of%20dues%20from%20the%20borrower%20in%20written-off%20loan%20accounts%20continues%2C%20write-off%20does%20not%20benefit%20the%20borrower%2C%20Karad%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20newspaper%20reported%20that%20the%20minister%20did%20not%20name%20individual%20borrowers%20whose%20accounts%20have%20been%20written%20off%20citing%20the%20RBI%20Act.%20Quoting%20RBI%2C%20he%20said%20that%20all%20SCBs%20have%20collected%20an%20aggregate%20amount%20of%20Rs%205%2C309.80%20crore%20as%20penal%20charges%2C%20including%20penalty%20charges%20against%20delay%20in%20payment%20of%20