ter%20all%20talking%20to%20adults%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Sarah%2C%20now%20training%20to%20professionally%20be%20an%20Indian%20Sign%20Language%20(ISL)%20interpreter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSign%20language%20was%20my%20first%20language.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F292576%2Fdeaf-mute-kashmiri-artist-carves-wooden-sculptures-earns-in-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoth%20my%20parents%20are%20Deaf%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20sign%20language%20is%20my%20mother%20tongue.%20That%20is%20how%20we%20communicate%20with%20each%20other%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fdeaf-and-Deaf.jpg-1700576818.png%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fdeaf-and-Deaf.jpg-1700576818.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fdeaf-and-Deaf.jpg-1700576818-300x126.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fdeaf-and-Deaf.jpg-1700576818-500x209.png%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fdeaf-and-Deaf.jpg-1700576818-768x321.png%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fdeaf-and-Deaf.jpg-1700576818-150x63.png%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334623%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22502%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%C2%A0For%20more%20information%2C%20please%20feel%20free%20to%20go%20through%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsignhealth.org.uk%2Fresources%2Flearn-about-deafness%2Fdeaf-or-deaf%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DWe%2520use%2520Deaf%2520with%2520a%2Clanguage%2520as%2520their%2520first%2520lan